var book = {
	"name": "Tirhthlah",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bawipa Theofilas, Ka cabu hmaisa sungah khan Jesuh in hnaṭuan hram a thawh ihsin vancungih lakso a si ni tiang,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> a thil tuahmi hmuahhmuah le a thuzirhmi hmuahhmuah kha ka ngan. Vancung ih lakso a si hlanah Amah ih a hrilmi a tirhthlah pawl cu Thlarau Thianghlim cahnak huham thawn ṭhatein thu a zirhta hai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A thih hnuah ni sawmli sung an hnenah voi tampi a lang ih a nungsal a si ti kha zohmanih el thei lo dingin phun tampi in a langter. Amah an hmu ih anih in Pathian Uknak thu kha an hnenah a sim.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule hmun khatih an tonkhawm awk laiah, an hnenah hiti in thu a pek: “Jerusalem ihsin khuihmanah feh hlah uh. Ka Pa in laksawng a lo pe ding tiah ka lo sim ciami kha hngak sawn uh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Johan cun tidai in baptisma a pe; asinain ni malte sungah Thlarau Thianghlim thawn baptisma pek nan si ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tirhthlah pawl cu Jesuh thawn an ton awk tikah annih in, “Bawipa, atuih caanah hin Israel mi hnenah Uknak cu na pe sal ding maw?” tiah an sut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Jesuh in an hnenah, “A cuih tikcu le nithla cu ka Pa ih thuneihnak ih khiah-mi a si ih nannih theih ṭulmi a si lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sikhalsehla nan hnenih Thlarau Thianghlim a rung thlen tikah cahnak huham thawn nan khat ding ih Jerusalem le Judea ram le Samaria ram hmuahhmuah le leilung tlun a deng tiang keimah ih theihpitu nan si ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutiih a sim ṭheh tikah Jesuh cu an mithmuh rori-ah vanah laakso a si ih mero in a phen ih an hmu thei nawn lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutiih a hung kainak van cu an zoh cuahco laiah puanvaar sinin mi pahnih hmakhatte-ah an kiangah an rung ding ih,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Galilee mi pawl, ziangah so van zoh in nan din cuahco? Nan hnen ihsin vanih a kaimi Jesuh hi vanih a kai lai nan hmuh vek cekci in a rakir sal leh ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Jesuh ih tirhthlah pawl cu Olif Tlang ihsin Jerusalem ah an kir. Olif Tlang cu Jerusalem ihsin peng hrek tluk a hlat.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Khawpi sungah an vung feh ih an umnak tlunta khaan ah an hung lut. Piter le Johan, Jeim le Andru, Filip le Thomas, Bartholomeo le Matthai, Alfias ih fapa Jeim, phun ṭantu Simon, le Jeim ih fapa Judas tla an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hmun khatih thlacam tlang dingah an tongkhawm ṭheu ih nunau pawl le Jesuh ih nu Mari le Jesuh ih naule pawl tla an tel.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ni malte a rei hnuah zumtu pawl an tongkhawm aw ih minung za le kul hrawng an si. Piter cu a ding ih,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ka u le ka nau pawl, Thlarau Thianghlim in David ih hmurka hmangin a sim ciami Jesuh a kaitu pawl hruaitu Judas ih thu cu Ca Thianghlim sungih an ngan vekin a kim a ṭul a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Judas cu kan hnaṭuanpi sungih tel ve dingah hrilmi a si ruangah kan pawl sungah sungtel a rak si ve,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> (Judas in thilsual a tuahmi manih a ngahmi tangka in lo pakhat a lei ih cuih lo sungah a bah ih a thi; a pum a kuai ih a sungril hmuah a pawt ṭheh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cuih thu cu Jerusalem ih a ummi hmuahhmuah in an thei ih anmah ih ṭong in cuih lo cu Akeldama an ti; a tican cu, “Thisen Lo,” tinak a si.)",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Piter in, “Ziangah tile Saam cabu sungah, ‘A inn cu lawng sehla A sungah zohman um hlah hai seh,’ tiah ngan ciami a um. Cule hmun dangah, ‘Midang in a hnaṭuan cu la hai seh,’ tiin a um fawn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Cuti a si ih Bawipa Jesuh thawhsalnak thutheitu-ah pakhatkhat cun in telpi a ṭul a si. Amah cu Bawi Jesuh kan hnenih khual a tlawn vivo sung hmuahhmuah kanmah lakah a tel ih, Johan in baptisma thu a simnak ihsin thokin Jesuh kan hnenin vanih laakso a si ni tiang, kanmah lakah a tel vemi a si ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Curuangah mi pahnih ih hmin an pek. Anmah cu Barsabbas ti ih kawhmi Josef, (Justus ti tla in an kawhmi) le Matthias an si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cule thla an cam ih, “Bawipa, nang cun mi thinlung sung na thei ṭheh; himi pahnih lakah zo deuh na hril ti run langter aw;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> a co dingmi hmunah in fehsantu Judas ih ai-awhtu ah na tirhthlah pawl lakih ṭuanvo la dingah na hrilmi cu run fiangter aw,” tiah an ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cule an pahnih sungah zoso tirhthlah a si ding ti theihnak ah camcawhfung an zuuk ih Matthias in a ngah. Matthias cu tirhthlah hleikhat pawl hnenah an betcih."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Pentikos ni a thlen tikah zumtu hmuahhmuah cu hmun khatah an um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hmakhatte-ah van ihsin thlipi hrang bangin thawmvang a rung ih an tonak khaan cu a khat ṭheh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule lei bangtuk a si mi meisa hliau an rungsuak zohzo ih cuih khaan sung ummi hmuahhmuah cuih meisa hliau cun a run dai fingfing.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> An zatein Thlarau Thianghlim in an khat ih Thlarau in ṭong theinak a pek vekin ṭong dangdang in an ṭong ciamco.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jerusalem khua sungah leilung tlun khuazakip ihsin a rami Judah mi an um laifang a si ih biaknak lam khalah a zuam ngaingaimi pawl an si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cuih ṭong dangdang ih an ṭongnak thawmvang an theih tikah miburpi an ra khawm aw. Zumtu pawl ih ṭongmi cu a rami pawl in anmah ih ṭong ciarin an theih tikah an mang a bangzet.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mangbang le khawruahhar in, “Hitiih a ṭong reromi pawl hi Galilee mi an si ko lo maw?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ziangtin so kanmah ih ṭong cio ih ṭong in kan theih thei?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kannih cu Parthia ram, Media ram, Elam ram, Mesopotamia ram, Judea ram, Kappadosia ram, Pontas ram, Asia ram,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Frizia ram, Pamfilia ram, Izipt ram le Libia ramsung Sairin khua kiang tla in a rami kan si. Mihrek cu Rom khua in a rami kan si ih,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Judah mi le Zentail mi Judah biaknak ih a lutmi pawl kan si. Mihrek cu Krete tikulh le Arabia ram in kan ra. Asinain Pathian in a huham thawn thil mak zetzet a tuahmi thu anmah ih ṭong ih an simmi kha kanmah ih ṭong ciarin kan thei a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mangbang le awloksong in, “Himi hi a tican ziang a si pei?” tiah pakhat le pakhat an sut aw rero.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Asinain midang cun zumtu pawl cu an hnihsan ih, “Hi pawl hi zu an ri a si hi!” tiah an ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule Piter cu a dang tirhthlah hleikhat hnenah a ding ih aw ring zetin misenpi hnenah thu a sim: “Ka phunpi Judah mi le Jerusalem ih a ummi pawl, nan zatein in ngai uhla, hi thil ih a tican ka lo sim hai ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nan ruah bangtuk a si lo; hipawl hi zu an ri lo; zinglam nazi pakua lawng a si lai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ziang so a si ti ahcun profet Joel ih a rak sim ciami a kimnak sawn a si. Profet Joel ih sim ciami cu:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ‘Pathian in, ni netnak lamah cun hiti in ka tuah ding; Mi hmuahhmuah parah ka Thlarau ka burh ding; Nan fapa pawl le nan fanu pawl in ka thu an phuang ding; Nan tlangval pawl in langnak an hmu ding; Nan patar pawl in mang an man ding;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Asi, ka salnu le ka salpa pawl tlun khalah cuih ni ahcun Ka Thlarau ka burh ding ih, ka thu an sim ding.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tlunlam vanah hmuhsaknak mak ka tuah ding ih, Hnuailam leilung par khalah khawruahhar ka tuah ding. Thisen le meisa le meikhu sahzet a um ding.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ni a thim ding ih, thlapi khi thisen bangin a sen ding; Bawipa ih Ni - ni maksak le ni sunglawi a thlenhlan deuh ah,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bawipa hnenah bomnak dil in a autu cu rundam an si ding,’ a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Ka phunpi Israel mi pawl, hi thu ka simmi hi ngaihnik uh! Nazareth mi Jesuh cu minung asinain Pathian ih thuneihnak a nei a si, ti cu amah hnenin Pathian in a huham thawn thil khawruahhar le hmuhsaknak mak zetzet a tuahmi pawl ihsin a langter zo. Himi cu nanmah rori ih nan theihmi a si, ziangahtile nan lakih a cangmi thil an si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Pathian amah ih khawkhannak vekin nan kut sungah Jesuh pek ding kha a rak ruahcat ciami a si. Misual pawl ih forhfialnakin Jesuh cu thinglamtah ah nan khenbet ih nan that.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sikhalsehla Pathian in thihnak ihsin a thoter sal ih thihnak huham sung ihsin a luatter zo, ziangahtile amah cu thihnak ih kaitar theihmi a si lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> David in amah ih thuhla cu hiti in a sim: ‘Bawipa cu ka mithmai ah ka hmu ringring; Ka kiangah a um ih ka phang lo ding.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Curuangah ka lung a awi ih, ka ṭongkam cu nomnak in a khat. Curuangah kei hi a thi theimi milai ka si naón, ruahsannak sungah hnangam zetin ka cawl ding.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile mithi khua-ah cun i taanta lo ding ih, rintlak na salpa hi thlankhur sungah ziamralta dingah cun i siang lo ding.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nunnak thlen theitu lamzin cu i hmuh zo ih i umpi ruangah lungawinak in ka khat ding,’ a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Ka u le ka nau pawl, mi hminthang kan pu Siangpahrang David ih thu cu nan hnenah fiangtein ka sim duh. David cu a thi ih an phum; a thlaan tla tuihsun tiang kan lakah a um.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Amah cu profet a si ih Pathian ih a kam ciami thu a thei; David bangtuk in David ih tesinfa pakhatkhat kha siangpahrang si dingah Pathian in thu a kam.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Pathian in hmailam caanah ziang a tuah ding ti cu David in a hmu cia; curuangah Messiah a thawhsalnak ding thu cu hiti in a sim: ‘Mithi khua ah amah cu a taanta lo ding ih, a taksa ruangpi cu thlaan sungah a ziamta lo ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Pathian in hi Jesuh rori hi thihnak ihsin a thoter sal ih cumi theihpitu cu kanmah hi kan si.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Pathian a Pa ih vorhlam kapah sunglawi zetin thlenter a si zo ih a kam cia bangtuk in Thlarau Thianghlim cu a Pa hnen ihsin a ngah zo. Atuih nan hmuhmi le nan theihmi cu kan parih a burhmi amah ih laksawng a si.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ziangahtile vancungih a thlengtu cu David a si lo; David amah in: ‘Bawipa in ka Bawipa hnenah, na ral pawl na ke hnuai ah,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na kepal-ih ka canter hlantiang Ka vorhlam kapah hin to aw, a ti,’ tiah a ti.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Israel mi pawl, thinglamtah parih nan thahmi Jesuh hi Pathian in Bawipa le Messiah ah a tuah zo a si, tihi fiangtein nan theih ṭheh dingah a ṭul hrimhrim a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Cuih thu an theih tikah an thinlung a khoih zetih Piter le a dang tirhthlah pawl cu, “U le nau pawl, ziangso kan tuah ding?” tiah an sut.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Piter in an hnenah, “Nan zatein nan sual sir fingfing uhla Jesuh Khrih hmin in baptisma lak uh; cuticun nan sualnak ngaidam nan si ding ih Pathian laksawng Thlarau Thianghlim nan ngah ding.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ziangahtile Pathian thukamnak cu nanmah le nan faate pawl hnenah le Pathian thawn a hlat awmi an si naón Bawipa kan Pathian in a kawhmi pawl hmuahhmuah hnenah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Piter in thu tampi a zirh ih a forh hai. “Hi miṭha lo parih a thleng dingmi hremnak ihsin luat dingah zuam aw uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Piter ih simmi cu mi tampi in an zum ih baptisma an lak; cuih ni ni khatah an pawl cu mi thawngthum tlukin an karh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> An zatein tirhthlah pawl hnen ihsin an zir ih, tirawl eitlangnak le thlacam tlangnak thawn pawlkomnak an nei ringring.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Tirhthlah pawl in khawruahharza le hmuhsaknak mak zetzet thil tampi an tuah ruangah mi hmuahhmuah ih thinlung sungah ṭihnak le hmaizahnak in a khat.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu an pawlkom aw ih thurual zetin an thil neihmi tla an ṭawm aw.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> An thilri neihmi le an hlawnthil pawl tla an zuar ih an ngahmi tangka cu an ṭulnak vekin an zem aw.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ni khat hnu ni khat Biakinn sungah an tongkhawm aw; an inn ah rawl an ṭawm aw ih tangdornak le lungawi thanuam in an ei tlang.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Pathian an thangṭhat ih mi hmuahhmuah hnenin mithmai ṭha an ngah. Cule nitinte in Bawipa in an pawlah rundamnak ngahtu a bet vivo."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nikhat ah Piter le Johan cu thlacam tikcu zanlam nazi pathum ah Biakinn ah an feh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutawkih Kotka Mawi an timi ah suahkeh kezeng pa pakhat a rak um. Nitinte Biakinn ih a fehtu pawl hnen ihsin tangka dil dingah cuih kotka-ah cun an hei ret ṭheu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Piter le Johan an luh kha a hmuh tikah thil pakhatkhat pe dingah a dil hai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ṭhatein an zoh fel ih Piter in, “In hun zohhnik!” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ziangtal ka ngah pei maw, tiah beisei zetin a zoh hai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule Piter cun, “Tangka lo pek ding zianghman ka nei lo; asinain ka neihmi ka lo pe: Nazareth mi Jesuh Khrih hmin in tho awla feh aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule a vorhlam kut in a kaih ih a vun dirh. Hmakhatteah cupa ih ke le kebeu pawl cu an cak sal.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A hung tho lohli ih amahte in a ding ih a feh thei. Cule Piter le Johan hnenah Biakinn sungah a lut ve. A feh, a khir a zuang ih Pathian a thangṭhat.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutiih a feh thei le Pathian a thangṭhat cu mipi in an hmu ih,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kotka Mawi ah tangka dil in a um ringringtu a si kha an theih tikah a parih thil a thlengmi ruangah an khawruah a har ih an mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cupa cu Solomon Hulhliap timi ahcun Piter le Johan hnenah a um kha an hmuh tikah mipi cu an khawruahhar in an hnenah an va tlan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cumi cu Piter in a hmuh tikah an hnenah, “Ka phunpi Israel mi pawl, ziangah so hi thu ah nan khawruah a har ih kanmah lehlam mitṭhep loin in zoh? Hi pa a feh thei hi kanmah ih cahnak le Pathian duhzawng in a nung theitu kan si ruangih a cangmi ah maw si nan ruat?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Abraham le Isaak le Jakob ih Pathian, kan pu le kan pa pawl ih Pathian in amah ih sunlawinak cu a Siahhlawh Jesuh hnenah a pek zo. Asinain nannih in amah cu thuneitu pawl ih kut sungah nan pek. Pilat in thlah dingih thu a rel ciami hman amah ih mithmuh rori-ah nan hnong zo a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Jesuh hi mi thianghlim le mi ṭhazet asinain nannih in nan hnong; cuih tlunah Pilat kha zaangfah nan dil ih laithattu kha thlah sawn dingah nan fial.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nannih cun nunnak ih mi a hruaitu kha nan that; asinain Pathian in thihnak ihsin a thoter sal ih kanmah hi cumi a theihpitu kan si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hi Jesuh hminih huham ruangah hi kezeng pa hin damnak a ngah thei. Nan hmuhmi le nan theihmi hi a hmin zumnak thawngin tuahmi a si. Nan zate ih nan hmuh ṭheh vekin Jesuh zumnak in hi pa hi a damter a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Curuangah ka u le ka nau tla, nanmah le nan hotu pawl in Jesuh parih nan rak tuahmi hi nan theih lo ruangih tuahmi a si ti ka thei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Pathian in khuahlan laipi ah a hrilmi Messiah cu harsatnak a tuar ding tiah profet pawl hnenin a rak phuang zo; cumi kha atu-ah hiti in a kim a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sir aw uhla Pathian hnenah kir sal uh. Cuti asile nan sualnak a lo ngaithiam ding. Cutiin nan ti asile,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bawipa hnen ihsin tharthawhnak tikcu a rathleng ding ih nan hrangih a hrilcia mi Messiah timi Jesuh cu nan hnenah a lo pe ding.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Pathian in khuahlan laipi ih a profet thianghlim pawl hnen ihsin a phuan cia vekin, ziang hmuahhmuah siam thar tikcu a kim hlanlo Jesuh cu vancungah a um ding.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ziangahtile Moses in, ‘Bawipa nan Pathian in keimah i thlah vekin nan miphun a si mi profet pakhat nan hnenah a thlah ding. Amah ih a lo simmi hmuahhmuah cu nan thlun ṭheh a ṭul.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cuih profet a thlun duh lotu cu Pathian miphun sung ihsin dawihlo a si ding ih siatsuahnak a tong ding,’ a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cule thuthan ding a neitu profet hmuahhmuah, profet Samuel le amah hnu ih a rami profet pawl khal in, an zatein tuih hrawngih a cangmi hi an rak than cia zo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Profet pawl hnen ihsin Pathian ih thukamnak cu nanmah ih hrangah a si ih Pathian in nan pu le nan pa pawl hnenih a tuahmi thukamnak a ṭawm vetu nan si. Pathian in Abraham hnenah, ‘Na tesinfa sung ihsin leilung tlunih mi hmuahhmuah cu thluasuahnak ka pe ding,’  tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cuti a si ruangah Pathian in zovek khal nan ṭhat lonak ihsin nan kir ih a lo thlawsuah theinak dingah a hrilmi a Siahhlawh cu a hmaisabik ah nan hnenah a thlah a si,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Piter le Johan in mipi hnenih thu an sim rero laiah puithiam ṭhenkhat le biakinn kilvengtu hotu bawi le Sadusi hrekkhat an ra thleng.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mithi pawl an nung sal ding ti fiangternak ah Jesuh cu thihnak ihsin a tho sal tiah tirhthlah pahnih ih an phuan ruangah annih pawl cu an thin-ai a thok ngaingai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah cuih tirhthlah pahnih cu an kai ih khua a sim zo ruangah thawngah a thaisun tiang an thlak.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla an thusimmi a theitu tampi cun an zum; a zumtu pawl cu an karh sinsin ih thawngnga tluk an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A thaisun ah Judah mi hotu pawl, upa pawl le Daanthiam pawl cu Jerusalem ah an tongkhawm aw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cutawkah Puithiam Saang Annas an tong; cule Kaiafas le Johan le Alexander le Puithiam Saang ih sungkhat dang pawl tla thawn an tongkhawm aw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tirhthlah pahnih cu an hmaiah an dinter ih, “Hi thil cangmi hi ziangtinso nan tuah? Ziang huham so nan neih ih zo ih hmin so nan hman?” tiah an sut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Piter cu Thlarau Thianghlim in a khat ih an hnenah, “Mipi hotu pawl le upa pawl,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> tuihsun ahhin hi kezeng pa a damnak thu le a parih thil ṭha tuah a si thu hi in sut a si ahcun,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> nan theih dingmi le Israel mi hmuahhmuah in an theih ṭheh dingmi cu hihi a si: nan hmaiih a dingmi pa a damfelnak hi Nazareth mi, thinglamtah parih nan thahmi, thihnak ihsin Pathian in a thawhter salmi Jesuh ih hmin thawngin a si, tihi a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Jesuh thu ahhin Ca Thianghlim in: ‘Inn saktu pawl in nan hnonmi lungto cu a thupi bik lungto ah a cang zo,’ tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Rundamnak cu amah ih sung lawngah a um; ziangahtile Pathian ih rundammi kan sinak dingah leikhawvel pumpuluk ah hin minung hnenih pekmi hmin dang zohman an um lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Khonsil upa pawl in Piter le Johan cu fimnak le thiamnak a nei lomi mi menmen an si naón ziangtlukin an ral a ṭha ti kha an hmuh tikah an mang a bang ngaingai. Cule annih cu Jesuh ih rualpi an si ti kha an mang sal.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sikhalsehla an damtermi pa cu Piter le Johan kiangih a din ringring ruangah an ṭong theimi zianghman a um fawn lo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah an thurelnak khaan ihsin lengah an suahter hai ih anmah lawng in khaan sungah cun thu an rel.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Pakhat le pakhat cu, “Ziangtin so kan tuah ko sawh ding? Zohman ih an tuah thei lomi hmuhsaknak thilmak an tuah ti cu Jerusalem khawsung ih a ummi hmuahhmuah in an thei ṭheh zo ih zohman ih el theimi a si nawn lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sikhalsehla hi thu hi mipi hnenih a zai lonak dingah Jesuh hmin in zohnen hmanah thu sim nawn hlah uh, kan ti pei,” tiah an ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cule an ko kir hai ih, Jesuh hmin in zohman zirh lo ding le zohnen hmanah thu sim hrimhrim lo dingin an dawn.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Asinain Piter le Johan in, “Nanmah ih thu thlun maw Pathian ih thu thlun so Pathian hmaiah a dik sawn, nanmahte in ṭhen hnik uh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ziangahtile kanmah rori in kan hmuhmi le kan theihmi cu sim loin kan um thei lo,” tiah an ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Curuangah Khonsil upa pawl cun nasa sinsin in ralrinnak an pek hnuah an thlah. Mi hmuahhmuah in an lakih thil a cangmi an hmu ih Pathian an thangṭhat ruangah tirhthlah pawl hrem cu a cang thei lo ti kha an hmu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hmuhsaknak ah damnak a ngahtu pa hi kum sawmli tlun a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Piter le Johan cu an luat vete in an rualpi pawl hnenah an kir ih puithiam le upa pawl ih an simmi thu pawl cu an ruah hai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cumi cu zumtu pawl in an theih tikah hmunkhatte ah Pathian hnenah thla an cam ih, “Maw Cungnungbik Bawipa, van le lei le tipithuanthum le a sungih ummi hmuahhmuah a Tuahtu Bawipa,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Thlarau Thianghlim hmangin na siahhlawh kan pu David hnenin thu na sim ih: ‘Ziangah so Zentail mi pawl hi an ai a thawh? Ziangah so milai hin a ṭhahnem lomi mi phiarnak an tuah?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bawipa le Messiah dodal dingah, leilung siangpahrang pawl an tim an tuah ih, Uktu bawi pawl thawn hmun khatah an tongkhawm aw,’ tiin na rak ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile Herod le Pontius Pilat in Messiah ih na hrilmi na Siahhlawh Thianghlim Jesuh dodal dingah hi khawpi sungah hin Zentail mi pawl le Israel mi pawl thawn an tongkhawm aw ngaingai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na huham le na tumtahnak in a hung cang leh ding tiih na rak khiah ciami kimter ṭheh dingah an tong aw khawm a si.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Maw Bawipa, atuih in hro reromi tla hi nangmah in run thei hram awla kannih na sal pawl tla hin na thu cu ralṭha zetih kan sim theinak dingah in bawm hram aw.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mi damnak dingah na baan run pharh awla na Siahhlawh Thianghlim Jesuh hmin in hmuhsaknak le khawruahhar thil pawl tuah theinak in run pe hram aw,” tiah an ti.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Thla an cam ṭheh vete in cutawkih an tonkhawmnak inn cu a hnin thluh. Thlarau Thianghlim in an khat ih Pathian thu cu ralṭha zetin an sim.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Zumtu pawl cu thinlung le ruahnak rual aw zetin an umtlang. Zohman in a neihmi thilri kha, ‘Ka bulta a si,’ a ti lo; an neihmi hmuahhmuah kha pakhat le pakhat an ṭawm aw.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bawi Jesuh thawhsalnak thu cu tirhthlah pawl in a nasa zetmi huham thawn an sim ih Pathian in an zate parah thlawsuah tampi a run burh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> An lakah zohman a tlasam mi an um lo. Lo a neitu le inn a neitu pawl in an lo le an inn pawl cu an zuar ih an ngahmi tangka cu,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> tirhthlah pawl kutah an rak pek. Cule cuih tangka cu a ṭulnak vekin an zem vivo.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Cubangtuk in Saipras tikulh ih a suakmi Levi mi Josef in,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> a lo kha a zuar ih a ngahmi tangka cu tirhthlah pawl ih kut sungah a pek. Josef cu tirhthlah pawl in Barnabas tiah an ti. (Barnabas ti cu “Thazaang Petu,” tinak a si.)"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Asinain Ananias an timi pa le a nupi Sapfira cun an neihmi thilri kha an zuar ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> a nupi ih lungkimnak thawn tangka ṭhenkhat cu anmah ih hrangah an ret ih a taangmi cu tirhthlah pawl kut sungah an pek.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah Piter in, “Ananias, ziangah so Satan in a lo neh ih na thil zuarnak ih na ngahmi tangka a hrek cu suup tahrat in Thlarau Thianghlim na bum?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na thilri cu na zuar hlanah nangmah ih ta a si; na zuar hnu khalah na ngahmi tangka cu na ta thotho a si. Sikhalsehla ziangah so hi bangtuk tuah ding hi na thinlung hrimhrim in na ruah? Milai na bum a si lo, Pathian na bum a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cumi cu Ananias in a theih vete in a tlu ih a thi; cule cuih thu a theitu hmuahhmuah cu an tuk a sum ṭheh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tlangval pawl an rung ih a ruak cu an tuam ṭheh hnuah lengah an zawn ih an phum.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nazi pathum hnuah ziang a cang ti thei loin a nupi a ra ve.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Piter in, “Hi tangka hi nan thil nan zuarmi ihsin nan ngahmi tangka zate a si maw? I sim hnik!” tiah a sut. Sapfira in, “Asi, kan ngahmi zate a si,” tiah a sawn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah Piter in, “Ziang hrangah so na pasal thawn nan pahnih in Bawipa ih Thlarau hniksak dingah nan lung a kimtlang? Na pasal a phumtu tlangval pawl cu sangka kiangah an um lai; nangmah khal an lo zawn suak ve ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hmakhatte-ah anih khal Piter kehram ah a tlu ih a thi ve. Tlangval pawl cu an rung lut ih a thi zo ti kha an hmuh tikah a lengah an zawn ih a pasal thlaan kiangah an va phum ve.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kawhhran pumpi le cuih thu a theitu hmuahhmuah cu tuksum in an um.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mipi lakah cun tirhthlah pawl in hmuhsaknak le khawruahhar thil tampi an tuah. Zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu Solomon Hulhliap timi ah an tong khawm aw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Anmah cu midang in an porh zet naón a lenglam mi cu an lakah an tel ngam lo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sikhalsehla nunau siseh mipa siseh Bawipa a zumtu pawl cu an pawl ah tam sinsin in an lut.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tirhthlah pawl ih thil an tuahmi an hmuh ruangah mina tampi cu khawsung lamzin ah an zawn ih Piter a feh zawng ah mi ṭhenkhat tal a thlaam in hliap seh tiah ihkhun le pher parah an hlum vivo hai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule mi tampi cu Jerusalem kiangkap khua ihsin an ra ih mina siseh, khawsia polh mi pawl siseh, an rak zawn ih an zatein an dam thluh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Puithiam Saang le a rualpi pawl hmuahhmuah le cutawk hrawngih a ummi Sadusi pawl cun tirhthlah pawl kha an halhsik tuk ruangah thil pakhatkhat tuah an tum.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tirhthlah pawl kha an kai ih mipi thawng ah an thlak.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sikhalsehla cuih zanah cun Bawipa ih vancungmi in thawnginn sangka pawl cu a ong ih tirhthlah pawl cu a suah hnuah an hnenah,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “Va feh uhla Biakinn sungah dingin misenpi hnenah hi nuntharnak thuhla hi kimten va sim uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A sim vekin tirhthlah pawl cun an tuah ih zing thlapit ah Biakinn sungah an lut ih thuzirh an thok. Puithiam Saang le a rualpi pawl in Khonsil thurelnak thupi zet nei dingah Judah mi upa hmuahhmuah kimtein an ko khawm. Tirhthlah pawl thawnginn ihsin an hmaiih rak hruai dingah mi an hei thlah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla thawnginn bawi pawl an va thlen tikah thawnginn sungah tirhthlah pawl an hmu nawn lo; curuangah an kir ih Khonsil pawl an sim:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Thawnginn kan va thlen tikah tawh ṭhatein a hren aw ih a kiltu pawl khal in sangka ṭhatein an kil ko; asinain sangka kan ong tikah a sungah zohman an um lo,” tiah an ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cumi cu puithiam upa le Biakinn kiltu bawi in an theih tikah tirhthlah pawl ziang an cang, tiah khawruahhar in an um.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule mi pakhat a rung lut ih, “Ngaihnik uh! Thawng ih nan thlakmi pawl kha Biakinn ah an um ih mi an zirh rero a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Curuangah Biakinn kiltu ralbawi le a kuthnuai milai pawl cu an va feh ih tirhthlah pawl cu an va hruai kir. Hranhram in an hruai lo, ziangahtile misenpi in lungto in in deng pang ding ti an phang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Tirhthlah pawl cu an run luhpi ih Khonsil hmaiah cun an dinter. Cule Puithiam Saang in thu a sut.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Hi pa hmin in thu nan zirh nawn lo pei, tiah fek zetin thu kan lo pe zo ti nan thei lo maw? Asinain nan tuah thotho. Nan thuzirhmi cu Jerusalem nan khahter zo ih a thihnak thu khalah kanmah hi mawhphurtu ah in tuah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Piter le a dang dungthlun pawl in, “Milai thu hnakin Pathian thu kan ngai sawn ding.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nanmah in Jesuh cu thinglamtah parah nan khen that; asinain kan pupa pawl ih Pathian in thihnak ihsin a thoter sal zo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Pathian in a thoter sal ih Israel mi pawl sualsirnak tikcu an neih ih an sualnak tla ngaidam a sinak dingah Amah cu Pathian in Hruaitu le Rundamtu ah a vorhlamah a toter zo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hi thil hmuahhmuah a theihpitu cu kanmah hi kan si; kanmah lawng kan si lo, Pathian in amah ih thu a ngaitu pawl hnenah laksawngih a rak pekmi Thlarau Thianghlim tla hi thu theihpitu a si ve,” tiah an ti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cutiih an timi cu Khonsil sungtel pawl in an theih tikah an thin a heng tuk lawmmam ih tirhthlah pawl cu thah ṭheh an duh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sikhalsehla anmah lakah mi hmuahhmuah ih upatmi Daanthiam pa Farasi mi Gamaliel cu Khonsil hmaiah a hung ding ih tirhthlah pawl cu a lengih malte sung suahter dingah thu a pek.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Cule Khonsil upa hnenah cun, “Israel mi pawl, himi pawl parih thil nan tuahmi ah hin ralring uh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kan dung laiah Theudas an timi pa a hungsuak ih keimah hi mi menmen ka si lo, a ti ih mi zali in an thlun. Asinain amah cu an that ih a thluntu pawl cu an ṭekdarh ṭheh; cule a hnaṭuannak cu a cem ve.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Cuih hnuah mipum siar laiah Galilee mi Judas a hungsuak lala ih mi tampi in an thlun hluarhlo; asinain thah a si ve ih a dungthluntu pawl cu an ṭekdarh ṭheh lala.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Atuih thu khalah hin fiangtein ka lo sim, himi pawl tlunah hin zianghman tuah hlah uh. Umsan men uh! An tumtahmi le an tuahmi hi milai ih thokmi a si ahcun a hloral ko ding.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Sikhalsehla Pathian ih tuahmi a si ahcun nan neh thei cuang lo ding. Pathian dodaltu riangri ah nan cang thei,” tiah a ti. Curuangah Khonsil upa pawl cun Gamaliel ih ruahnak pekmi cu an thlun.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Tirhthlah pawl cu an ko ih fungfek in an vuak ih Jesuh hmin in thu sim nawn lo dingah thu an pek hnuah an thlah.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Tirhthlah pawl cu Khonsil upa pawl hnen ihsin an suah tikah Jesuh hrangah ningzah mualpho tuar dingin ruah an si ruangah an lung a awizet.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Cule nitinte in Messiah Jesuh ih Thuthang ṭha cu Biakinn ah siseh mi inn ah siseh catbang loin an zirh ih an sim vivo."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Caan malte a rei deuh tikah dungthluntu pawl an tam vivo ih Judah mi pawl le Grik ṭong in a ṭongtu Judah mi pawl karlak ah thubuai a um. Grik ṭong a hmangtu Judah mi pawl in nitin a ṭulmi leinak ih tangka zem tikah an nuhmei pawl in an co ding zat an co lo a si, tiah thu a um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah tirhthlah hleihnih pawl in zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu hmun khatah an kokhawm ih, “Tangka thuhla tawlrelnak ah Pathian thusim kan daithlang a si ahcun a dik lo ding.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah u le nau pawl, nanmah lakah Thlarau Thianghlim le fimnak in a khatmi mi pasarih hril uhla anmah pawl cu hi thuhla tawlreltu ah kan ret ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kannih cu kan tikcu zatein thlacamnak le thusimnak ah kan hmang ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tirhthlah hleihnih pawl ih ruahnak an suahpi mi parah an zatein an lung a awi ih cuticun zumnak le Thlarau Thianghlim in a khatmi Stefen, Filip, Prokhoras, Nikanor, Timon, Parmenas, le Antiok khua ihsin Judah biaknak ih a luttu Zentail mi Nikolaus tla an hril.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> An pasarih in tirhthlah pawl hnenah an fehpi ih tirhthlah pawl in an lu parah an kut an suang ih thla an cam sak.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule Pathian thu cu a zai vivo. Dungthluntu pawl tla Jerusalem khua sungah an karh vivo ih puithiam tampi in an zumnak cu an pom ve.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Pathian in a thlawsuah zetmi le cahnak huham thawn a khatmi Stefen in misenpi lakah khawruahharza le hmuhsaknak mak tampi a tuah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Asinain Salsuak pawl sungin Stefen thawn thu-el awknak a suak ih acuih Stefen thu eltu lakah cun Sairin khua le Alexandria khua ihsin a rami Judah pawl tla an tel. Cun Silisia le Asia ram ih Judah pawl khal an tel ve.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Asinain Stefen cu Thlarau in fimnak a pek ih a ṭong tikah cun zohman in an el thei lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Curuangah mi ṭhenkhat kha, “Moses le Pathian thangsiat in a ṭong kan thei a si,” tiah ti dingah nawhthuh an pek.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuti cun misenpi, upa pawl le Daanthiam pawl kha thinheng koin an forh. Stefen cu an kai ih Khonsil upa hmaiah an suahpi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule thuphan puhtu ding pawl cu an rak hruai ih annih in, “Hi pa in kan Biakinn Thianghlim le Moses Daan tla hi nautat hmuhsuam in a ṭong ringring.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hi Nazareth mi Jesuh in hi Biakinn hi a bal ṭheh ding ih Moses san ihsin kanmah ih san tiang a ummi kan pupa daan khal a thleng ṭheh ding a si, tiah a ṭong lai kan thei,” an ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Khonsil pumkhawmnak sungih a telmi hmuahhmuah in Stefen cu an hei zoh ih a mithmai cu vancungmi ih mithmai bangtuk in an hmu."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Puithiam Saang in Stefen cu, “Hitiih an timi hi a si ngaingai maw?” tiah a sut.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Stefen in, “U le nau, nu le pa pawl, i ngaihnik uh! Kan pu Abraham cu Haran um dingih a feh hlanah Mesopotamia ah Pathian sunlawinak a hnenah a rung lang ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ‘Na sungkhat le na ram taanta awla ka lo hmuh dingmi ramah feh aw,’ tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuti cun Khaldea ram ihsin a suak ih Haran khua ah a um. A pa thih hnuah atu nan umnak ramah hin Pathian in a certer.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Culai ah hi ram hi Pathian in Abraham hnenah a bulta si dingah a fiakte hman a pe lo; asinain a hnenah pe dingin thu a kam ih hi ram hi nangmah le na tesinfa pawl ih ta a si ding, tiah a ti. Pathian in hiti ih thukamnak a tuah laiah Abraham cu faate a nei lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Pathian in a hnenah, ‘Na tesinfa pawl cu ramdang ah an um ding; cuih ramah sal an cang ding ih kum zali sung zonzaih an tuar ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sikhalsehla an renmi miphun parah cun thuṭhennak ka nei ding ih cuih hnu lawngah cuih ram ihsin an suak ding ih hi hmunah hin keimah in bia ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule Pathian in Abraham hnenah serhtannak daan kha a thukam hminsinnakah a pek. Curuangah Abraham in a fapa Isaak a suah hnu zarh khatah a serh a tansak. Isaak in a fapa Jakob ih serh a tansak ih Jakob in a fapa hleihnih an serh a tansak. A fapa hleihnih cu kan phun cithlahtu kan pupa hminthang pawl an si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Jakob ih fapa pawl in an naupa Josef cu an nahsuah ih Izipt ramah salah an zuar. Sikhalsehla Pathian a hnenah a um ih,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> a harsatnak sung ihsin himte in a hruai suak. Izipt siangpahrang hmaiih a din tikah Pathian in Josef cu ziaza mawi le fimnak a pek ih Izipt siangpahrang in a ram pumpi le a innsang tlunah uktu bawi a ṭuanter.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Izipt ram le Kanaan ram sungih mangṭam a tlun tikah mipi hrangah harsatnak tampi a thleng. Kan pupa pawl khal in rawl an ngah thei lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Jakob in Izipt ah rawl a um ti a theih tikah a fapa pawl, kan pu le kan pa pawl cu a thlah; himi cu Izipt an thlennak hmaisa bik a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A voihnihnak ih Izipt an thlen tikah a u le hnenah Josef cu a phuang aw ih Izipt siangpahrang in Josef ih sungkhat pawl cu a thei ngah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Curuangah Josef in a pa Jakob le a sungkhat pawl hnenah Izipt ramih rung vai dingin thu a cah. An zatein minung sawmsarih le panga an si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule Jakob cu Izipt ah a vung feh; cutawkah amah le a fapa pawl cu an thi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> An ruak cu Shekhem ah an fehpi ih Abraham in Hamor miphun hnen ihsin tangka in a rak leimi thlaan ah an phum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Pathian in Abraham hnenih thu a kammi a kimnak tikcu a nai vivo tikah Izipt ramih a ummi kan phunpi pawl cu an tam sinsin.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Neta bikah Josef ih thuhla a thei dah lotu siangpahrang pakhat in Izipt ram cu a uk.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kan pu le kan pa pawl cu a bum ih a hrem; an faate pawl tla thi hai seh tiah an innsung ihsin inn lengah a hlonter.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Culai caanah naute mawi zet Moses timi cu a suak. Moses cu inn ah thla thum sung ṭhatein an cawm.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Pawnleng ih hlon a si ve tikah siangpahrang ih fanu in a lak ih a fapa ah a tuah ih cutiin a kilkhawi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Izipt mi ih fimnak hmuahhmuah an zirh thluh ih a ṭongkam le a tuahnak in mi nasazet a si ti a langter.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Moses cu kum sawmli a ti tikah a phunpi Israel mi pawl ziang bangtuk in an nung, ti hmuh duh ah a leng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Culai ah a phunpi Israel mi pakhat cu Izipt pa in a rak hrem kha a hmu tikah a va bawm ih phuba la in Izipt pa cu a that.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> (Pathian in anmah luattertu dingah i hmang ding ih ka phunpi khal in an theithiam ding, tiah a ruat naón an rak theithiam lo.)",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A thaisun ah Israel mi pahnih an sual awk lai kha a hmu ih va rem a tum. ‘Unau pawl, i ngai uh! Nannih cu mi phunkhat Israel mi veve nan si! Ziangah so hiti in nan sual awk rero?’ tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Sikhalsehla a phunpi a hmuhsuamtu pa in Moses cu a tulpet ih, ‘Zo in so kan tlunah uktu le thuṭhentu ah a lo tuah?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mizan ih Izipt pa na thah vek khan thah ve i duh maw si?’ tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cumi cu Moses in a theih tikah Izipt ram ihsin a tlan ih Midian ramah a va um. Cutawkah fapa pahnih a nei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Kum sawmli a liam hnuah Sinai Tlang kiang ramṭhing ah hrambur alh sung ihsin Moses hnenah vancungmi pakhat a lang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cuih mei alh cu Moses in a hmuh tikah a mang a bang ih zohhliah dingah hrambur alh-mi kiangah cun a va feh. Asinain Bawipa ih aw a thei ih,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ‘Keimah hi nan pupa pawl ih Pathian, Abraham ih Pathian, Isaak le Jakob ih Pathian ka si,’ tiah a ti. Moses cu thinphang in a khur ih a zoh hman a zoh ngam lo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bawipa cun, ‘Na kedam phuak aw, ziangahtile na dinnak hmun hi hmun thianghlim a si!",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Izipt ramih ka minung pawl an tuarmi le an zonzaihnak ka hmu. An aihramnak ka thei ih anmah luatter dingah ka rung. Ra aw, Izipt ah ka lo thlah ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Moses cu Israel mi pawl ih hnon dahmi pa a si. ‘Zo in so kan tlunah uktu le thuṭhentu-ah an lo tuah?’ tiah an rak ti. Hrambur alh sung ihsin a hnenih a langmi vancungmi ih bomnak thawngin Pathian in Israel mi uktu dingah le luattertu dingah a thlahmi a si.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Izipt ram ihsin Israel mi pawl cu a hruaisuak ih Izipt ram le Tipi Sen le ramṭhing lakah kum sawmli sung thil khawruahhar le hmuhsaknak mak tampi a tuah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Moses cu Israel mi hnenah, ‘Pathian in nan hnenah keimah i thlah bangtuk in profet a thlah ding ih cupa cu nanmah ih miphun sung ihsin a si ding,’ tiah a rak titu pa a si.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Amah cu Israel mi pawl ramṭhingih an um laiah an lakih a tel ringringtu pa a si; kan pu le kan pa pawl lakah a rak um ih Sinai Tlangah vancungmi ṭongkam a rak sangtu le misenpi hnenih a rak umtu a si; cule Pathian thunung kan hnenih a thlen theinak dingah a rak cohlangtu a si fawn.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> “Sikhalsehla kan pu le kan pa pawl in amah cu an thlun duh lo. An hnong ih Izipt ram ah vung kirsal an duh sawn.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Curuangah Aaron hnenah, ‘In hruaitu dingah khawzing tampi in in tuahsak aw. Izipt ram ihsin in hruaisuaktu Moses parah ziang a cang ti kan thei nawn ual lo,’ tiah an ti.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Cuti a si ruangah cawcang hmuihmel cuangin caw lem an tuah ih rai an thawi ih an kutih an tuahcopmi hrangah upatnak puai an tuah ciamco.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Curuangah Pathian in a dungtun ih profet pawl cabu sungih ngan a si vekin vanih arsi pawl a biakter hai. Cuih cabu sungah cun: ‘Israel mi pawl, kum sawmli sung ramṭhing ah ṭilva nan that ih Raithawinak nan pekmi kha ka hnenah nan tuahmi a si lo.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Nan phurhmi thlam cu Molek khawzing puanthlam a si. Nan kenmi milem cu nan khawzing Refan ih arsi lem a si. Annih tla cu biak dingih nan tuahmi khawzing lem an si. Curuangah nannih cu Babilon lan ah ka lo dawihlo ding,’ tiah a um.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Kan pu le kan pa pawl in Thukamnak Puanthlam cu nelrawn ramṭhing ah an nei ringring. Cuih Puanthlam cu Pathian in Moses hnenih a langtermi pianhmang vekih sakmi a si.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Neh hnuah kan pu le kan pa pawl in cuih puanthlam cu an pu pa hnen ihsin an lak ih Joshua thawn an feh tikah an fehpi vivo; hmai an nor ih Pathian in a rak um ciami miphun pawl kha a dawisak ih cuih ram pawl cu an lak vivo. Puanthlam cu cutawkah David san tiang a um.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> David cu Pathian hmaiah mithmai ṭha a ngah ih Jakob ih Pathian umnak hrangah inn pakhat sak thei dingah Pathian hnenah a dil.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Sikhalsehla inn a saktu ngaingai cu Solomon a si.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> “Asinain Cungnungbik Pathian cu minung kutih tuahmi inn sungah a um lo; Profet pawl in hiti in an sim:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> ‘Vancung hi ka tokham a si ih Leilung hi ka kepal a si, tiah Bawipa in a ti. Ka hrangah ziangbangtuk inn so sak nan tum? Ka um duhnak hmun cu khuitawk so a si?",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hi thil hmuahhmuah a tuahtu hi Keimah ka si lo maw?’ a ti.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> “Nan lung a va ruh lawmmam so! Nan thinlung cu Pathian thei lo thinlung a va si lai so! Pathian thu ngai dingah nan hna a va set lawmmam ve! Nannih hi nan pupa pawl vek thotho nan si: Thlarau Thianghlim nan dodal ringring!",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Nan pupa pawl ih an hrem lomi profet pakhat tal an um maw? Pathian ih Siahhlawh fel a ra ding tiah khuahlan lai ihsin a rak phuangtu Pathian ih palai pawl an rak that. Atu-ah cuih a felmi a Siahhlawh cu nanmah in nan zuar ih nan that!",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Vancungmi in an run kenmi Pathian ih daan a saangtu cu nanmah nan si; asinain cuih daan a thlun lotu cu nanmah thotho nan si,” tiah a ti.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Khonsil upa pawl in Stefen thusimmi an theih tikah an thin a heng tuk ih an hacang an rial hnawh.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Sikhalsehla Stefen cu Thlarau Thianghlim in a khat ih vancung a hun zoh tikah Pathian sunlawinak le Pathian vorhlamih a dingmi Jesuh kha a hun hmu.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Cutikah, “Zohhnik uh! Van a ong aw ih Pathian vorhlamah Milai Fapa a ding ka hmu!” tiah a ti.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Cutikah Khonsil upa pawl cu an hna an kut in an phit ih an aw neih patawp in an au ih Stefen cu an zon!",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Khawpi sung ihsin an dirhsuak ih lungto in an deng. A dengtu pawl in an puan pawl cu Saul an timi tlangvalpa hnenah an retta.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Lungto in an den rero laiah Stefen cun Bawipa a ko ih, “Bawipa Jesuh, ka thlarau run la hram aw!” tiah a au.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> A khuk a bilh ih, “Bawipa, an sualnak hi ciing ringring hram hlah aw!” tiah napi in a au. Cutiih a au ṭheh vete in a hnuk a cat."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih ni ihsin thokin Jerusalem ih kawhhran cu hremnak nasa zet an tuar. Tirhthlah pawl siarlo a dang zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu Judea ram le Samaria ram sungah an ṭhendarh aw ṭheh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Stefen cu Pathian a ṭihzahtu ṭhenkhat in an vui ih nasa zetin an ṭah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Asinain Saul cun kawhhran pawl siatsuah a tum; inn khat hnu inn khat a feh ih nunau mipa tilo zumtu hmuahhmuah an inn ihsin a dirsuak ih thawng ah a thlak hai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A ṭekdarhmi zumtu pawl cu khuazakipah an thleng ih an thlennak hmunkipah Thuthang ṭha an sim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Filip cu Samaria khawpi ah a feh ih cuih khuami hnenah Messiah ih thuhla a sim.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mi tampi in a thusimmi cu ṭhatein an ngai ih hmuhsaknak a tuahmi tla an hmu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Miburpi sung ihsin khawsia pawl ringpi ih au phah in an suak ih mizeng le ke-awl pawl tla an dam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Curuangah cuih khawpi sungah lungawinak tampi a um.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutawk khua ah Simon an timi pa a rak um. Caan rei nawn a mitkher thiamnak in Samaria mi pawl cu an thinlung let ko in a tuah. Keimah ka si bik tiin a ruat aw ve.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khawpi sungih a ummi hmuahhmuah a tum a seen in a thu an ngai. Annih in, “Amah hi, ‘A Maksak mi Huham,’ timi Pathian ih cahnak a si hi!” tiah an ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Caan reipi a mitkher thiamnak in an lung let ṭheh ko in a tuah ruangah a thu an thlun duhnak a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sikhalsehla Filip ih thusimmi Pathian Uknak Thuthang ṭha le Jesuh Khrih ih thuhla an theih tikah an zum ih nunau siseh mipa siseh baptisma an lak.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Simon khal cun a zum ve; baptisma a lak hnuah Filip cu a thlun ih khawruahhar le hmuhsaknak thil tampi Filip ih tuahmi kha a hmuh tikah anih khal a mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Jerusalem ih a ummi tirhthlah pawl in Samaria mi khal in Pathian thu an pom ve thlang ti an theih tikah an hnenah Piter le Johan an thlah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> An hnen an thlen tikah zumtu pawl in Thlarau Thianghlim an ngahnak dingah an hrangah thla an cam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ziangahtile Thlarau Thianghlim kha zo ih hnen hmanah a rung thleng hrih lo; Bawi Jesuh hminih baptisma latu lawng an si lai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule Piter le Johan in an parah kut suangin thla an cam ih Thlarau Thianghlim an ngah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tirhthlah pawl in an kut an suan tikah zumtu pawl in Thlarau Thianghlim an ngah kha Simon in a hmu. Curuangah Piter le Johan hnenah,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Kei khal in an tlunih ka kut ka suanmi hmuahhmuah Thlarau Thianghlim an ngah theinak dingah hi cahnak huham i pe ve uh,” tiah ti phah in tangka a pek hai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sikhalsehla Piter in, “Pathian ih pekmi laksawng hi tangka thawn lei thei dingih na ruah ruangah nangmah cu na tangka thawn va hloral uh!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Pathian mithmuh-ah na thinlung a dik lo ruangah kan hnaṭuanmi sungah na tel lo, covo khal na nei lo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hi bangtuk thil ṭha lo na ruah sualnak ihsin siir aw awla a lo ngaithiamnak dingah Bawipa ih hnenah thlacam aw.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ziangahtile nahsuahnak in a khatmi le sualnak thawng sungih a tlami na si, tihi ka hmu a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cutikah Simon in Piter le Johan hnenah, “Zaangfahnak in hi nan ṭongmi pawl hi ka parih a thlen lonak dingah Pathian hnenah thla i cam sak hram uh,” tiah a dil.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Pathian thu an phuang ih an hmuhmi le an tonmi an sim hnuah Piter le Johan cu Jerusalem ah an kir sal. An kir phahah Samaria peng khawte tampi sungah Thuthang ṭha cu an sim vivo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bawipa ih vancungmi in Filip hnenah, “Na timtuah awla thlanglam ah Jerusalem ihsin Gaza fehnak lamzin ah vung feh aw,” tiah a ti. (Atu-ah cun hi lamzin cu an hmang nawn lo.)",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> A ti vekin a tim a tuah ih Filip cu a feh. Culai ah Ethiopia mi pakhat an khua lamih a tlungmi a tong. Cupa cu tilpermi a si ih Ethiopia siangpahrang nu ih neihmi sumsaw hmuahhmuah a kilkhawitu bawi a si. Amah cu Jerusalem ah Pathian bia dingin a feh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> A ra tlunlam ah a rangleng parah to in profet Isaiah cabu a siar.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Thlarau Thianghlim in Filip hnenah, “Feh awla khi rangleng khi va naih aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Filip cun a hei dawi ih profet Isaiah cabu a siar ti a thei. Filip in, “Na siarmi hi a tican na thei maw?” tiah a sut.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cupa cun, “Zotal ih in simfiang lo ahcun ziangtinso ka theih thei ding?” tiah a sawn. Cule Filip cu a rangleng parah to ve dingin a sawm.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> A siarmi Ca Thianghlim cu a tanglam vek hin a si: “Amah cu thah dingmi tuu bangin an hruai ih, Tuu faate a hmul an met laiah ai loih a um bangin, ṭong loin daitein a um.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hmuhsuam nautatnak a tuar, ṭantu zohman a nei lo; Leitlun ihsin a nunnak an laksak ruangah, A ci thlahmi pawl sim ding zohman an um lo,” tiin a um.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Cupa in Filip cu, “I sim hnik! Profet Isaiah ih a ṭongmi hi zo ih thu so a si? Amah ih thu maw, midang ih thu so?” tiah a sut.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Cutikah Filip in cuih Baibal caang ihsin thokin Bawi Jesuh Thuthang ṭha cu a sim ṭheh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Cutiin an vung feh vivo ih tidai a umnak hmun an thleng. Cupa cun, “Hinah tidai a um. Baptisma co dingah ziangso i dawntu a um?” tiah a ti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> (Filip in, “Na thinlung zatein na zum ahcun baptisma co ding na si,” a ti. Cupa cun, “Ka zum; Jesuh Khrih cu Pathian Fapa a si tiah ka zum,” a ti.)",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cuih Ethiopia pa cun a rangleng cu a dinter ih Filip thawn tidai sungah an vung ṭum ih Filip in baptisma a pek.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Tidai sung ihsin an hung suah tikah Bawipa ih Thlarau in Filip cu a lak hlo. Cuih bawi in Filip cu a hmu nawn lo; asinain lungawi zetin a inn lamah a tlung.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Filip cu Ashdod a va thleng; Sisaria ah a feh ih lamzin tluan khua kipah Thuthang ṭha cu a sim vivo."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih caan hrawngah Saul cun Bawipa ih dungthlun pawl kha that dingah a hringhro rero. Puithiam Saang hnenah a va feh ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Damaskas khua ih sinakok inn uktu pawl in amah kha an rak theihnak dingah ca ken ding a va dil. A tumtahmi cu cutawkah Bawipa ih Lamzin a thluntu an um asile nunau mipa tilo kai tahratin Jerusalem ih hruai ding kha a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Saul cu Damaskas khua a thlen zikah hmakhatte ah van ihsin tleunak in a kimvelin a run tlet.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Saul cu a tlu ih, “Saul, Saul, ziangah so i hrem?” tiah aw pakhat a thei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Saul in, “Bawipa, zoso na si?” tiah a sut. Cuih aw cun, “Na hrem reromi Jesuh ka si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tho awla khawpi sungah va feh aw; na tuah ṭulmi kha an lo sim ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Saul thawn khual a tlawngmi pawl cu an cawl ṭheh ih kam khat hman an ṭong lo; aw cu an thei naón zohman an hmu lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Saul cu leilung ihsin a hung tho ih a mit a hun meng, asinain zianghman a hmu thei lo. Curuangah a kut in an hruai ih Damaskas khua sungah cun an fehpi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ni thum sung khua a hmu thei lo; cuih ni thum sungah zianghman a ei lo, tidai khal a in lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Damaskas khawsungah Ananias timi dungthluntu pakhat a um. Langnak hmuhmi a nei ih cumi sungin Bawipa in, “Ananias!” tiah a ko. Anih in, “Bawipa, hinah ka um,” a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bawipa in, “Na tim tuah awla Lamzin Ding timi ah va feh aw. Judas inn ah Tarsas khuami Saul timi pa a um maw, tiin va sut aw. Amah cu thla a cam lai rero;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> anih khal in langnak a hmu ih cumi langnak sungah cun a mit khua a hmuh thei salnak dingah Ananias an timi pa a rung lut ih a lu parah kut a ra suan kha a hmu,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ananias in, “Bawipa, mi tampi in himi pa ih thuhla hi in sim zo ih Jerusalem ih na minung pawl parih thil ṭha lo a tuahmi pawl khal in sim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule atu-ah puithiam upa pawl ih thuneihnak thawn nangmah a lo biatu pawl hmuahhmuah kai dingah Damaskas ah a ra thleng a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bawipa in a hnenah, “Va feh aw! Ziangahtile amah cu Zentail mi hnen le siangpahrang pawl hnen le Israel mi pawl hnenah ka hmin thangter dingin le ka hnaṭuan dingin ka hril zo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule keimah in ka hrangih a tuar dingmi pawl cu ka hmuh ding a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Curuangah Ananias cu a feh ih Saul umnak innah cun a va lut. Saul ih lu parah a kut suang tahrat in, “Unau pa Saul, hitawk lam na rat laiih lamzinah na hnenih a langmi Jesuh Bawipa amah rori in na hnenah i thlah. Khua na hmuh sal theinak dingah le Thlarau Thianghlim thawn na khahnak dingah na hnenah i thlah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hmakhatte-ah Saul ih mit ihsin ngakep bangtuk a si mi a tla ih khua a hmu thei sal. A tho ih baptisma an pek.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule rawl a ei ih thazaang a nei sal. Saul cu Damaskas khua ih dungthluntu pawl hnenah ni malte sung a um.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> An pumkhawmnak sinakok inn pawlah a va feh ih Jesuh cu Pathian Fapa a si, ti thu kha a sim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A theitu hmuahhmuah cu an mang a bang ngaingai ih, “Jerusalem ah Jesuh a zumtu pohpoh a siatsuahtu cu amah hi a si lo maw? Cuvek thothoin hitawk khalah hin cubangtuk mi cu kai tahratin puithiam upa pawl hnenih thlenpi dingah a ra thleng a si lo maw?” tiah an sut aw ruri.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla Saul thusimmi cu hmual a nei deuhdeuh; Jesuh cu Messiah rori a si tiah a simmi kha mi thinlung sungah fiangtukin a luh ruangah Damaskas khua ih a ummi Judah mi pawl in a thu cu an let thei lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ni tam nawn a rei tikah Judah mi pawl an tongkhawm aw ih Saul that dingah khua an khang.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Asinain cutiih an khawkhanmi cu a simtu an rak um ih Saul in a thei. Amah thah duh ah a sun a zan in khawpiih kotka pawl cu an kil.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sikhalsehla Saul a thluntu pawl in zan khatah Saul cu bawm sungah an ret ih khawpi kulhnak hauhruang ong in a lengah an vun ṭhum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Saul cu Jerusalem ah a feh ih dungthlun pawl lakah tel ve a tum. Asinain annih pawl cun dungthlun a si ve thlang ti kha an zum lo ih an zatein amah kha an ṭih riangri.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cule Barnabas in a ṭanpi ih tirhthlah pawl hnenah a fehpi. Barnabas in an hnenah cun Damaskas lamzin ih Bawipa a tonnak le Bawipa in a hnenih a ṭongmi pawl kha fiangtein a sim. Cule Saul in Jesuh ih hmin kha Damaskas khua ah ralṭha zetin thuthang.tha a phuannak thu tla a sim.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Curuangah Saul cu an hnenah a um ih Jerusalem khawsung hmunzakip ah a feh ih ralṭha zetin Jesuh hmin in thu a sim.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Grik ṭong a hmangtu Judah mi pawl hnen tla-ah thu a sim ih thu tla an el aw, asinain annih cun a thah an tum.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cumi cu zumtu pawl in an theih tikah Saul cu Sisaria ah an hruai ih Tarsas ah an thlah.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cuti cun Judea ram, Galilee ram le Samaria ram sung kawhhran pawl cu hnangamte in an um. kawhhran cu Thlarau Thianghlim bomnak in a cak deuhdeuh ih mi khal an karh vivo. Pathian ṭihzah in an um.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Piter cu khuazakipah a tlawng ih voikhat cu Lidda khua ih ummi Pathian awi pawl tlawng dingah a feh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cutawkah Aenias an timi pa a tong. Aenias cu mizeng a si ih kum riat sung ihkhun ihsin a tho thei dah lomi a si.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Piter in, “Aenias, Jesuh Khrih in a lo damter a si. Tho awla na ihphah zual aw,” tiah a ti. Hmakhatte-ah Aenias cu a tho.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Lidda le Sharon-ih a ummi hmuahhmuah in Aenias cu an hmuh ruangah Bawipa lamah an hoikir.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Joppa khua ahcun Tabitha an timi nu a um ih Jesuh zumtu a si. (A Grik hmin cu Dorkas a si ih a tican cu “Zukneng,” tinak a si.) A tikcu hmuah cu thil ṭha tuahnak ah le mifarah bomnak ah a hmang.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Cuih caanah cu nu cu besia zetin a na ih a thi. A ruak cu an kholh ih tlunta khaan ah an ret.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Joppa khua cu Lidda khua in a naite a si. Cule Joppa ih a ummi zumtu pawl in Lidda ah Piter a um ti kha an theih tikah mi pahnih an thlah ih, “Zamrang in kan hnenah ra hram aw,” tiah an cah.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Curuangah Piter cu a tim a tuah ih anmah a thlun. A va thlen tikah Piter cu tlunta khaanah cun an hruai. Cutawkah cun nuhmei pawl in an pan ciamco ih an ṭap ih Dorkas damlai-ih angki le kawtkor a tahmi pawl kha an hmuh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Piter in khaan sung ihsin mi pawl cu a suahter ṭheh ih, a khukbil in thla a cam; cule Dorkas ruak lam a hoi ih, “Tabitha, tho aw!” tiah a ti. Dorkas cun a mit a hun meng ih Piter a hmuh tikah a hung to.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Piter in a hei dawh ih a dinter. Cule nuhmei pawl le zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu a kawh ih a nungzo tiin an hnenah a hmuh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Cuih thu cu Joppa khawsung hmuahhmuah ah a thang ih mi tampi in Bawipa an zum.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Piter cu Joppa khua ah savun tuahtu Simon inn ah ni tampi sung a caam."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Sisaria khua ah Kornelias an timi pa a um. Amah cu, “Italy Ralkap Burpi,” timi Rom ralkap bu uktu ralbawi bothum a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amah cu Pathian a ṭihzah zettu a si; a innsungsang in Pathian a bia ringringtu an si. Judah mi mifarah pawl tampi a bawm ih cat loin Pathian hnenah thla a cam ringringtu a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Voikhat cu zanlam nazi pathum tlukah langnak a hmu; cuih a hmuhmi ahcun Pathian ih vancungmi pakhat a hnenah a ra ih, “Kornelias!” tiah a ko.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuih vancungmi cu ṭih phah in a zoh ih, “Ziang so a si, Bawipa?” tiah a sut. Vancungmi cun, “Pathian cu na thlacammi le mifarah na bomnak parah hin a lung a awi ih na dilnak a thei a si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Curuangah Joppa khua ah Simon Piter an timi pa ko dingin mi thlah aw.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Simon Piter cu Tipi kapih a ummi savun in thil tuahtu Simon ih innah a caam,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule vancungmi cu a feh; cuih hnuah Kornelias in a innih a ummi hnen-um pahnih le ralkap pakhat a ko. Ralkap pa cu biaknak lamah a taimazet le a felzetmi a si ih amah a kilvengtu lakah pakhat a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Thil a cangmi pawl hmuahhmuah kha a sim ṭheh hnuah Joppa khua ah a thlah hai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A thaisun ahcun an feh vivo ih Joppa khua an thlen zik zawng sunlaifang hrawngah Piter cu thlacam dingin inn parah a hung kai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Piter cu a ril a rawng ih rawl ei a duh; rawl an tuah rero laiah langnak a hmu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Van khi a ong aw ih puan hlaipi bangtuk a si mi thil pakhat a kil pali in leilung ah an run ṭhummi a hmu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A sungah ke li nei ramsa a phunphun, bokvak ramsa le vate a phunphun an um.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Aw pakhat in a hnenah, “Piter, tho aw; that awla ei aw!” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Asinain Piter in, “Bawipa, a si lo! A thiang lomi le a borhhlawhmi ka ei dah hrimhrim lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Aw cun a run sim sal ih, “Pathian in a thiang a timi cu a thiang lo-ah ruat hlah,” tiah a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cumi cu voithum tiang a rung lang ih cuih hnuah cuih thil cu vanah lak kir a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cuih langnak ih a tican cu Piter in a ruah rero laifangah Kornelias ih thlahmi pawl cu Simon ih inn an thleng ih kotka lengah an ding.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “hittawk ah Simon Piter timi mikhual a um maw?” tiah an vun auh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Piter cun a hmuhmi ih tican a ruah rero laifangah Thlarau in, “Ngaihnik, mi pathum in an lo hawl!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na timtuah awla vung feh aw; cule an hnenih feh ding cu ṭhukṭhun in um hlah; keimah ih thlahmi an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Curuangah Piter cu a vung ṭum ih a ra hawltu hnenah cun, “Nan hawlmi cu keimah ka si. Ziang so nan ṭul?” tiah a sut.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Annih in, “Ralbawi Kornelias in in thlah. Amah cu miṭhazet a si. Pathian a bia ih Judah mi pawl in an upat zetmi a si. Sim ding na neihmi kha thei seh tiah a inn ah nangmah lo sawm dingin Pathian ih vancungmi in a fial,” tiah an ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Piter in cuih zan cu a hnenih riak hrih dingin a sawm hai ih an riak. A thaisun ah Piter cu a tim a tuah ih anmah thawn a feh; Joppa khua ih Khrih zumtu hrekkhat pawl tla an tel ve.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A tipsun ah Sisaria ah a thleng ih Kornelias cun a sungkhat pawl le a sawmmi a rualpi pawl thawn an rak hngak ringring.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Piter cu inn ih a vung luh zawng ah Kornelias in a rak hmuak ih a hmaiah a kuun ih a kehram ah a bok.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asinain Piter in a dinter ih, “Ding aw! Kei khal minung sokhaw ka si ve,” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Inn sungih an luh phahah Piter in Kornelias cu a biak phah vivo; inn sungah cun mi tampi an tong-aw khawm.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Piter in an hnenah, “Kan biaknak daan vek a si ahcun Judah mi in Zentail mi leen ding le pawl ding cu khammi a si, ti cu nan thei ṭheh. Sikhalsehla zohman mi thiang lo le mi borhhlawh-ah ruah ding a si lo ti kha Pathian in i hmuh zo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Curuangah mi nan thlah ih in ra kawh tikah kam khat hman el loin ka ra. Ziangah in ko ti atu-ah hin i sim hnik uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kornelias in, “Kan dunglam ni thum laiah, tuih tikcu hrawng zanlam nazi pathum ah ka innah thla ka cam. Hmakhatte-ah hnipuan tleu zet hrukin mi pakhat ka hmaiah a ding ih,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ‘Kornelias, Pathian in na thlacamnak a thei ih mifarah na bomnak khal a hminsin ṭheh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Joppa ah Simon Piter an timi pa ko dingin mi thlah aw. Joppa ahcun Tipi kapih a um mi savun in thil tuahtupa Simon ih inn ah a riak,’ tiah i ti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Curuangah hmakhatte-ah ka lo ko; cule nangmah khal in i zaangfah ih na ra. Atu-ah hitawk ah hin Pathian hmaika-ah kan zatein kan um ih Bawipa in sim dingih a lo fialmi kha ngai dingah kan lo hngak a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Piter cun a thok ih, “Pathian cun zozo khal bangraan tein mi a zoh a si, ti thudik kha ka thei.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ziangbangtuk miphun a si khalle Pathian a ṭihzah ih a hmaiah thildik a tuah a si ahcun Pathian ih pom tlak a si.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Mi hmuahhmuah ih Bawipa a si mi Jesuh Khrih hnenin daihnak Thuthang ṭha cu Pathian in Israel mi hnenah a pek, ti cu nan thei.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Johan in baptisma thuthang a sim hnu Galilee ihsin thokin Israel ramsung hmunzakip ah thil maksak a cangmi khal cu nan thei ṭheh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nazareth mi Jesuh parah ziang bangtuk in Pathian in Thlarau Thianghlim le huham a burh ti tla nan thei ṭheh. A hnenah Pathian a um ruangah hmunzakip ah feh tahrat in thil ṭha a tuah vivo ih Satan ih tuahsiatmi pawl hmuahhmuah a damter thluh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Israel ram sungah le Jerusalem ih a tuahmi hmuahhmuah a hmutu le a theitu kanmah hi kan si. Cule amah cu thinglamtah parah an khen ih an that.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Sikhalsehla ni thumnak ni ah Pathian in thihnak ihsin a thoter sal ih kan hnenah a langter.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Mi hmuahhmuah hnenah si loin a thu theitu dingih in hrilmi pawl hnenah a langter. Thihnak ihsin a thawhsal hnuah amah thawn kan ei kan in tlang a si.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Cule mi hnenah Thuthang ṭha sim dingah le amah cu Pathian in a nungmi le a thimi parah thuṭhentu ih a tuah kha simtu dingah in fial a si.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Profet hmuahhmuah in amah ih thu cu an sim ih amah a zumtu hmuahhmuah in a hmin thawngin an sualnak ngaidam a si ding, tiah an ti,” tiah a sim.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Cutiih Piter a ṭong rero laiah a thusimmi a ngaitu hmuahhmuah parah Thlarau Thianghlim a rung thleng.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Joppa ihsin Piter thawn a rami Jesuh zumtu Judah mi pawl cu Zentail mi hnen khalah Pathian in a laksawng Thlarau Thianghlim a burh ti kha an hmuh tikah an mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ziangahtile cute pawl cu ṭong phun dang in an ṭong ih Pathian ih maksak zia an thangṭhat kha an theih ruangah a si. Piter in,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> “Kanmah ih kan ngah zo vekin himi pawl khal in Thlarau Thianghlim an ngah ve a si. Curuangah tidai ih baptisma la ding kha zo in so a dawn thei ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Curuangah Jesuh Khrih hmin in baptisma lak dingah thu a pek. Cule an hnenih caam hrih dingin Piter cu an sawm."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tirhthlah pawl le Judea ram sungih a ummi zumtu hmuahhmuah in Pathian ih thu cu Zentail mi pawl khal in an pom ngah zo, ti an thei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Piter cu Jerusalem ih a thlen tikah Zentail mi pawl serhtanter a duhtu pawl in an soisel ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Serhtan lo Zentail pawl innah na riak ih an hnenah rawl tiangin na ei,” an ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cuti a si ruangah Piter in thil a cangmi umtudan hmuahhmuah kha a hramthok ihsin a sim hai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Joppa khua ih thla ka cam laiah langnak hmuhmi ka nei. Van ihsin kil li nei puan hlaipi bangtuk a si mi thil pakhat ka kiangte-ah an run ṭhum.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A sung ṭhatein ka vun bih ih ramsa le innzuat ṭilva le a bokvak thiammi thilnung le hramlakih vate pawl ka hmu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule aw ka thei ih cuih aw cun, ‘Piter, tho aw, that awla ei aw,’ tiah i ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Asinain kei in, ‘Bawipa, a si lo! Biaknak lamin a thiang lo timi le a borhhlawhmi rawl ka kaa sungah an lut dah kel lo,’ tiah ka ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah van ihsin aw ka thei sal ih, ‘Pathian in a thiang, a ti ciami kha nang in a thiang lo tiah ruat hlah,’ tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuti cun voithum tiang rori a cang ih neta bikah a zatein vanah an lak kir sal.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cuti a si laiah Sisaria ihsin an rak thlahmi mi pathum kha ka riahnak inn ah an ra thleng.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule zianghman nuarnak um lotein feh dingah Thlarau in i fial. Hi Joppa khua mi kan unau paruk, Jesuh zumtu pawl khal hin Sisaria ahcun in thlun ve ih kan zatein Kornelias ih inn ah kan va feh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kornelias in vancungmi a rung ih a innih a dinnak thu kha in sim. Cuih vancungmi cun Kornelias hnenah, ‘Joppa ah mi thlah awla a hmin ngai Simon Piter an timi pa koter aw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amah in thu a sim ding ih cuih a thusimmi thawngin nangmah le na innsang rundamnak nan ngah ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule thusim ka hun thawh ih a hramthok ih kan parih Thlarau Thianghlim a rung thlen vekin an parah Thlarau Thianghlim cu a thleng ve.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah Bawipa in, ‘Johan cun tidai thawn baptisma a lo pek; asinain nannih cu Thlarau Thianghlim thawn baptisma pek nan si ding,’ tiah a rak timi ka vun mang sal.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Pathian in Bawipa Jesuh Khrih kan zum ih kan hnenah Thlarau Thianghlim cu laksawngih in rak pek bangtuk in hi Zentail mi hnen khalah cuih laksawng cu a pek ve a si, ti cu a fiang zetmi a si. Ziangtin so kei taak ko hin Pathian cu ka kham thei ding!” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cumi an theih tikah an soiselnak cu an baang ih Pathian thangṭhat in, “Pathian in Zentail mi hnen khalah sualsir awknak le nunnak caan a pek ve a si cu!” tiah an ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Stefen an thah hnu hremnak a um ruangah Jesuh zumtu pawl ṭhenkhat cu khuazakip ah an ṭekdarh ṭheh. Mi tampi cu Fonisia, Saipras le Antiok tiang an thleng ih Judah mi hnen lawngah Thuthang ṭha cu an sim.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sikhalsehla zumtu ṭhenkhat cu Saipras le Sairin khua ihsin Antiok khua ah an feh ih Bawi Jesuh Khrih ih Thuthang ṭha cu Zentail mi hnen khalah an sim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bawipa ih huham an hnenah a um ih mi tampi in an zum ih Bawipa ih lam an pan.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cuih thuhla cu Jerusalem khua a thleng ih Jerusalem ih kawhhran in Antiok khua ah Barnabas an hun thlah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Barnabas cu Antiok khua a thlen tikah Pathian in mipi hnenih thlawsuah a pekzia a hmuh tikah a lung a awi ngaingai ih an thinlung zatein Bawipa an zum ih rinsantlak zumtu an si theinak dingah thazaang a pek hai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Barnabas cu miṭhazet a si ih Thlarau Thianghlim le zumfeknak thawn a khatmi a si. Cule mi tampi Bawipa ih hnenah a hruai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule Barnabas cu Saul hawl dingah Tarsas ah a feh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Saul a hmuh tikah Antiok ah a fehpi ih kum khat sung an pahnih in kawhhran minung pawl kha an pumkhawmpi ih mi tampi an zirh. Hi Antiok khua ah hin a si dungthlun pawl cu “Khristian” tiin an kawh hmaisa bik.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cuih caan hrawngah profet ṭhenkhat pawl cu Jerusalem ihsin Antiok ah an feh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> An lakih profet pakhat Agabas an timi pa a ding ih Thlarau huham thawn, “Leilung pumpuluk ah mangṭam a tlung ding a si,” tiah a sim. (Cuih mangṭam cu Klaudius in Rom siangpahrang a ṭuan laiah a thleng.)",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Dungthluntu pawl cun an tithei tawk ciar in Judea ramih a ummi zumtu unau pawl bomnak pe dingah an tawlrel.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> An tawlrel vekin an ngahmi tangka kha Barnabas le Saul kut in kawhhran upa hnenah an kuat."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hi caan hrawngah Siangpahrang Herod in kawhhran sungih Khristian ṭhenkhat pawl hrem a thok.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Johan unau Jeim kha ralnam hmang-in a thahter ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> cumi cun Judah mi pawl an lung a awiter ti a hmuh tikah Piter khal a kaihter. (Himi cu Thilnu tello Sang Puai tuah laifangah a si.)",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Piter cu an kai ih thawngah an thlak; thawnginn kiltu ralkap bur li an um ih bur khatah ralkap pali fingfing an um; cu pawl ih kil dingin an kut sungah an pek. Lantak puai ṭheh tikah zapi hmaiah a thu cu rel dingin Herod ih tumtahmi a si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuti cun Piter cu thawng sungah an ret, asinain a hrangah kawhhran pawl in Pathian hnenah napi in thla an camsak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Herod in a thaisun mipi hmaiah Piter ih thu ka rel ding a ti ni zanah Piter cu thawnginn kiltu ralkap pahnih karlakah a it. Thir cikcin pahnih in an khih ih thawnginn kotka khal an kil ṭheh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Rinlopi-ah Bawipa ih vancungmi a rung ding ih an ihnak khaan cu tleunak in a run tleuter. Vancungmi in Piter cu a liang in a hnin ih, “Zamrang in tho aw!” tiah a ṭhang. Hmakhatte-ah Piter ih kut ihsin thir cikcin cu an poihtla.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule vancungmi in, “Na taikhap khap awla na kedam dam aw,” tiah a ti. A tivek cun Piter in a tuah ih vancungmi in, “Na puan sin awla i thlun aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Piter cun a thlun ih thawnginn lengah an suak; vancungmi in cuti ih a tuah cu thungai a si dingah a ruat lo; langnak ka hmu a si ding, tiah a ruat aw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ralkap ih an kilnak kotka pakhatnak cu an lan, cule a pahnihnak tla an lan thotho. A netnak ah khawpi sung thawn a peh-awmi thir kotka an thleng. Cuih kotka cu an hrangah amahte in a ong aw ih an pahnih in an suak. Lamzin an vun zawh ih rinlopi ah vancungmi cun a hlohsan ih Piter lawng a taang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah a parih a cangmi thil pawl cu fiangtein a hun thei ngah ih, “Atu cu a cangmi ngaingai a si ka thei zo! Herod thuneihnak sungin le Judah mi pawl in ka parih cang dingin saduh an thahmi hmuahhmuah sung ihsin runsuak dingah Bawipa in a vancungmi a run thlah a si hi!” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Thil a cangmi a theih ngah hnuah Johan Marka ih nu Mari ih inn ah a feh; cutawkah mi tampi an khawm aw ih thla an cam rero.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Piter cun a leng ihsin sangka a vun king ih Roda timi hnen-um nu cu sangka ong dingin a ra.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Piter ih aw a si ti a theih tikah a lung a awi tuk ih sangka hman ong loin, “Inn lengah Piter a ding a si!” tiah a au.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Annih in, “Na aa maw si?” tiah an ti. Sikhalsehla, a si ngaingai sokhaw, a ti ringring ruangah, “A vancungmi a si pei cu!” an ti thotho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Piter in sangka cu cat loin a king rero. A net-ah sangka cu an ong ih Piter a si kha an hmuh tikah an mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Piter cun daiteih um dingin a zaa a zaap ih, Bawipa in thawng sung ihsin a suahnak thuhla kha an hnenah a sim. “Hi thu hi Jeim le a dang zumtu pawl sim uh,” tiah a ti ih a suak ih hmun dangah a feh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zinglam khua a van tikah thawnginn kiltu ralkap pawl cu, Piter ziang a cang a si pei, tiah an buai nasa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Piter hawl dingah Herod in thu a pek; asinain an hmu lo. Curuangah thawnginn kiltu pawl cu an thu a zingzoiter ih that dingin thu a pek. Cuih hnuah Judea ram ihsin Herod cu a suak ih Sisaria khua ah caan tawkfang a hmang.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Herod cu Tai-ar le Sidon mi pawl parah a thin a heng ngaingai; curuangah cuih khuami pawl cu Herod tong dingah a bur in an feh. A hmaisabik ah siangpahrang innih hotu bik Blastas kha an hnenih ṭang dingin an sawm. Cule Herod hnenah cun an va feh ih daihnak le remnak tuah dingin an va dil. Ziangah cutiin an dil tile an rammi pawl ih rawl an ngahmi cu Herod siangpahrang ukmi ram sung ihsin a rat ruangah a si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> An ni tinh ni ah Herod cu a siangpahrang thilthuam in a thuam aw ih a tokham ah a to ih mipi hnenah thu a sim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cutikah mipi in, “Hitiih a ṭongtu hi milai a si ual lo, pathian a sisi!” tiah an au.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hmakhatte-ah Bawipa ih vancungmi in Herod cu natsiava in a natter, ziangahtile Pathian kha upatnak a pek lo ruangah a si. Herod cu a rulkhuk in a sunglam an ei thluh ih a thi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Pathian ih thu cu a zai ih a ṭhang vivo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Barnabas le Saul cu an hnaṭuan dingmi an ṭuan ṭheh ruangah Jerusalem ihsin Johan Marka an hruai ih an kir."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Antiok khua kawhhran sungah profet le saya ṭhenkhat an um. Anmah tla cu Barnabas, Simeon (Midum ti tla in an ti), (Sairin khua mi) Lusias, (Mangki Herod thawn a ṭhang tlangtu) Minian le Saul an si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Anmah pawl cu Pathian bia in rawl an ulh laiah Thlarau Thianghlim in, “Barnabas le Saul hi ka thiahmi hnaṭuan lawng ṭuan dingah thiadang uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Rawl ul in thla an cam hnuah an lu parah an kut an suang ih Barnabas le Saul cu an hei thlah.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Thlarau Thianghlim in a thlah hai bangtuk in Barnabas le Saul cu Seleusia ah an feh ih cutawk ihsin tangphawlawng in Saipras tikulh ah an lan.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Salamis khua an thlen tikah Judah mi pawl ih sinakok ah Pathian thu an sim. An hnaṭuan bawmtu dingah Johan Marka an hruai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Saipras tikulh sung an tlawng vivo ih Pafos khua tiang an thleng. Cutawk ah mitkher thiam Bar-Jesuh an timi an tong. Amah cu Judah mi, profet a ti awmi a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Amah cu Saipras tikulh uktu Mangki Serzias Paulas ih rualpi a si. Serzias Paulas cu mifim zet a si. Pathian thu theih a duh ruangah Barnabas le Saul cu a hnenah a ko.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Asinain mitkher thiam Elimas in a ngaih lo; (Elimas ti cu a Grik hmin a si.) Serzias Paulas kha an simmi zum lo dingin a forh ciamco.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule Saul, Paul ti tla in an kawhmi, cu Thlarau Thianghlim in a khat ih Paul in mitkher thiam pa cu hmaiton tein a zoh ih,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Nang Satan fapa! Thilṭha hmuahhmuah a dodaltu cu nangmah na si. Mi bumnak ṭha lo a phunphun in na khat ih Bawipa ih thudik hi thuphan ih canter ding lawnglawng na zuam a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Atu rori-ah hin Bawipa ih kut cu na parah a rung thleng ding, na mit a caw ding ih tawkfang sung cu sun khawvang na hmu lo ding,” tiah a ti. Hmakhatte-ah Elimas ih mit cu mero dum in a khuh ih amah hruaitu ding hawl ah mitcaw cingin a vak rero.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutiih a cangmi cu Mangki bawipa in a hmuh tikah zumtu-ah a cang; ziangahtile Bawipa ih thuhla an zirhmi ah a mang a bang ngaingai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Paul le a rualpi pawl cu tangphawlawng in Pafos ihsin an feh ih Pamfilia ram Perga khua an thleng. Cutawk ihsin Johan Marka in a kirsan ih Jerusalem ah a tlung.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Perga ihsin an feh sal ih Pisidia ram Antiok khua an thleng. Cutawkah Sabbath ni ah sinakok ah an feh ih an to.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A khawmmi pawl in Moses Daan cabu le profet pawl ih nganmi cabu an siar hnuah sinakok hotu pawl in, “Unau pawl, kan mipi hrangah thapeknak ṭongkam sim ding nan neih asile in sim uh,” tiah an ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Paul cu a ding ih a kut hawi phah in thusim a thok: “Ka phunpi Israel mi le hitawk ih Pathian a ra biami Zentail mi hmuahhmuah tla, i ngai uh!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Israel ih Pathian in kan pu le kan pa pawl a hril ih Izipt ramih an um laiah miphun tumpi ah a tuah. Cuih Pathian cun Izipt ram ihsin a maksak mi a huham thawn a suah hai ih,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> nelrawn ramṭhing lakah kum sawmli sung a zoh, a kilkhawi hai a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kanaan ramih a rak ummi miphun phun sarih kha a siatsuah ṭheh ih amah ih miphun Israel mi cu ram luahtu ah a tuah.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hitiih thil a cangmi hi kum zali le sawmnga sung a rei. Cuih hnuah profet Samuel san a thlen hlan sung Thuṭhentu pawl a ret.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule Israel mi pawl in siangpahrang an dil ih Pathian in kum sawmli sung an siangpahrang si dingah Benjamin hrin sungin Kish ih fapa Saul a pek hai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cun Saul a dawihlo hnuah Pathian in David kha an siangpahrang ah a tuah. David thu cu Pathian in hiti in a ti: ‘Jesse ih fapa David cu ka mi duhzawng a si. Ka tuahter duhmi hmuahhmuah kha a tuah ding a si,’ tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cule David ih tesinfa Jesuh cu a rak kam cia vekin Pathian in Israel mi pawl Rundamtu dingah a tuah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Jesuh ih hnaṭuan a thok hlan deuh ah, Johan in Israel mi hmuahhmuah hnenah an sual sir aw ding le baptisma la dingah thu a sim.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule Johan in a hnaṭuan a ṭuan ṭheh zik zawng ah mipi hnenah, ‘Zo a si tiin so in ti?’ tiah a sut. ‘Nan hngak reromi cu kei ka si lo! Asinain ngai uh! Amah cu keimah hnuah a ra ding ih kei cu a kedam hri phoihtu ding hmanah ka tlak lo,’ tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka phunpi Israel mi, Abraham ih tesinfa pawl le hitawk ih Pathian a ra biatu Zentail mi pawl, hi rundamnak Thuthang hi kan zate hrangih pekmi a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile Jerusalem ih a rak ummi mipi pawl le an hotu pawl in Jesuh cu Rundamtu a si tiah an rak thei lo. Profet pawl ih rak nganmi thu Sabbath tinte in an siarmi khal a tican an thei lo. Asinain Jesuh an thahnak in profet pawl ih ṭongkam kha an kimter a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cule annih in Jesuh an thah theinak dingah thuhla an hawl rero naón, an hawl thei lo ruangah Pilat hnenah thahnak thu pe ding in an dil.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cun Ca Thianghlim in a thuhla a rak sim ciami hmuahhmuah kha an tuah ṭheh hnuah thinglamtah par ihsin an ṭhum ih thlaan ah an phum.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Sikhalsehla Pathian in thihnak ihsin a thoter sal ih,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> amah thawn Galilee ihsin Jerusalem tiang khual a tlawngtu pawl hnenah ni tampi sung a lang. Atu-ah Amah ih ai-ah cupawl cu Israel mi hnenah thutheitu an si.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Cuih Thuthang ṭha cu atu-ah nan hnenah kan rak keng. Pathian in kan pupa pawl hnenih thu a rak kammi cu atu an tesinfa kannih hnenah hin Jesuh thihnak ihsin a thoter salnak thawngin a kimter zo a si. Cumi cu Saam pahnihnak sungah: ‘Nangmah cu ka Fapa na si, tuihsun ah na Pa ka si zo,’ tiin a um.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Cule Jesuh cu thlaan sungah a thu-ralta lo ding ih a thosal ding ti thu-ah Pathian in hiti in a sim cia. ‘David hnenih kam ciami a thianghlimmi thluasuahnak cu nanmah hnenah ka lo pe ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Cule hmun dang khalah, ‘A thianghlimmi na siahhlawh cu thlaan sungah na ziamralter siang lo ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ziangahtile David cu amah ih san sungah Pathian duhmi hna a ṭuan ve naón, a thih tikah a pu le a pa hnenah an phum ih a taksa cu thlaan sungah a ziamta a si.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sikhalsehla Pathian in thlaan ihsin a thawhter mipa-ih parah cun cubangtuk in a si lo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ka phunpi Israel pawl, nan zatein fiang zetih nan theih a ṭul mi cu: Jesuh hmin in sual ngaidamnak thuthang nan hnenah phuan a si; nan sualnak sung ihsin Moses ih Daan in a lo luatter thei lo, asinain Jesuh a zumtu hmuahhmuah cu an sualnak sung ihsin an luat a si, tihi nan theih a ṭul.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Cuti a si ruangah ralring uh, a tanglamih profet pawl ih an rak simmi hi nan parah a kim pang ding. Profet pawl in:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ‘Zohhnik uh! Nannih mi hnihsan hmang pawl: Mangbang thinphang uhla thi ta uh! Ziangahtile tuihsun ih ka tuahmi hi, mi in nan hnenih an simfiang hmanah nan zum duh lo dingmi thil an si,’ tiin an sim,” tiah a ti.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Paul le Barnabas cu sinakok ihsin an suak ih mipi pawl cun hmai Sabbath ni ih ra sal dingin le cuih Thuthang ra sim sal dingin an sawm.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Mipi pumkhawmnak ihsin an ṭiak hnuah Paul le Barnabas cu Judah mi tampi le Judah biaknak ih a lutmi Zentail mi tampi in an thlun. Tirhthlah pawl in an hnenah thu an sim ih Pathian zaangfahnak sungih nung ringring dingin thazaang an pek hai.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> A hmaizarh Sabbath ni ah mi tampi, khawsung mi hmuahhmuah titlak in Pathian thu theih duh ah an ra suak.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Cumi cu Judah mi pawl in an hmuh tikah an nahsuak ih Paul ih thusimmi cu an el ih an hmuhsuam.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul le Barnabas cun ralṭha sinsin in thu an sim. “Pathian thu nan hnenih sim hmaisa ding cu a ṭulmi a si. Sikhalsehla nannih in nan duh lo, nan el ih kumkhua nunnak ngah ding tlak ih nan ruat awk lo ruangah kan lo tlansan ding ih Zentail mi hnenah kan feh ding.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Ziangahtile Bawipa ih thukham in pekmi cu hiti in a si: ‘Leilung pumpuluk hi rundam a sinak dingah, nannih cu Zentail mi hrangah tleunak ah ka lo tuah zo a si,’ a ti,” tiah an ti.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Cuih thu cu Zentail mi pawl in an theih tikah an lung a awi ngaingai ih Bawipa ih Thuthang ṭha cu an sunloih zet. Cule kumkhua nunnak hrangih hrilmi pawl cu zumtu-ah an cang.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bawipa ih thu cu cuih ramsung hmunkipah a thang.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Sikhalsehla Judah mi pawl in khawsungih upa pawl le Pathian awitu upat tlak Zentail nunau pawl kha an tokhrok ih cu pawl cun Paul le Barnabas cu an hrem ih an peng sung ihsin an dawihlo.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Paul le Barnabas cun an parih lungkim lonak langternak ah an ke ih leidip kha an thingta ih Ikoniam ah an feh.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Antiok khua ih dungthlun pawl cu lungawinak le Thlarau Thianghlim in an khat."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cubangtuk thotho in Ikoniam khua khalah Paul le Barnabas cu sinakok ah an va feh ih nasa zetin thu an sim. Judah mi le Zentail mi tampi zumtu-ah an cang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asinain a zum duh lotu Judah mi pawl in Zentail mi pawl kha an tokhrok ih zumtu pawl kha an dodalter.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Tirhthlah pahnih cu cutawkah reipi an um ih ralṭha zetin Bawipa ih thu an sim rero. Bawipa ih zaangfahnak thu an simmi a dik a si, ti langternak ah Bawipa in hmuhsaknak mak le khawruahhar thil tuah theinak huham a pek hai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Khawsung mi pawl cu an ṭhen aw ṭheh. Mihrek in Judah mi an ṭan ih mihrek in tirhthlah pawl an ṭan.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule Zentail mi ṭhenkhat le Judah mi ṭhenkhat in an hotu pawl thawn tirhthlah pawl tuahsiat ding le lungto in deng dingah thu an relcat.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cumi cu tirhthlah pawl in an theih tikah Likaonia ram sungih Listra khua, Derbe khua le a kiangkap ram pawl ah an tlan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutawkah Thuthang ṭha cu an sim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Listra khua ah mizeng pakhat, suahkeh ke-awl ih voikhat hman a feh thei dah lo pa a um.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Paul thusimnak ahcun a to ih a thusim cu a ngai. Paul in a thusimmi kha cupa in a zum ih damnak a ngah thei ti a hmuh tikah hmaitontein a zoh ih,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ringzet in, “Tho awla dingtein hung ding aw!” tiah a ti. Cupa cu a hung khir ih a feh thei!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutiih Paul ih a tuahmi cu mipi in an hmuh tikah anmah Likaonia ṭong in, “Khawzing pawl minung bangtuk ah an cang ih kan hnenah an rung a si hi!” tiah an au ciamco.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Barnabas kha an khawzing Zeus hmin an pek ih Paul cu a ṭong biktu a si ruangah an khawzing Hermes hmin an pek.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An khuahnar ah an khawzing Zeus ih biakinn a um; cutawkih puithiam in cawcang pawl le pangpar pawl kotka ah a run keng, ziangahtile amah le mipi pawl in tirhthlah pawl hnenah raithawinak pek an duh ruangah a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutiih tuah an tummi cu Barnabas le Paul in an theih tikah an hnipuan an thlek ih mipi lakah au phah in an tlan vivo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Hitiin ziangah so nan tuah tum? Kannih hi nanmah bangtuk milai kan si ve! A ṭhahnem lomi thil nan tuahnak ihsin lei le van le tipithuanthum le a sungih ummi hmuahhmuah a tuahtu Pathian nung hnenih nan kirnak dingah Thuthang ṭha sim dingin kan ra a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hlanlaiah cun Pathian in zozo khal an duhmi lamzin thlun dingin a on.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sikhalsehla thilṭha a tuahmi in amah a um ti kha a langter ringring a si: van ihsin ruah a surter ih a tikcu caan ah thlaici kho a umter; tirawl a lo pek ih nan thinlung hnangam in a tuah a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutiin an sim hnu hmanah raithawinak tuah lo dingah tirhthlah pawl in misenpi cu har zetin an kham thei ceu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Judah mi ṭhenkhat Pisidia ram Antiok khua in le Ikoniam khua ihsin an ra ih miburpi kha anmah lam ṭang dingin an sawm ngah hnuah Paul cu lungto in an deng; a thi zo tiah an ruat ih hnarpawn ah an hnuk ih an taan.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sikhalsehla dungthluntu pawl a kiangah ding in an tonkhawm awk tikah a tho ih khawsungah a feh sal. A thaisun ah Barnabas thawn Derbe khua ah an feh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Paul le Barnabas in Thuthang ṭha cu Derbe khua ah an sim ih dungthluntu tampi an ngah. Cuih hnuah Listra khua, Ikoniam khua le Pisidia peng Antiok khua ah an kir.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Zumtu pawl kha tha an pek phah vivo ih zumnak sungah rintlak zetin um dingin an forh vivo. “Pathian Uknak sung lut ding kan si ahcun harsatnak tampi kan ton ding hrimhrim a si,” tiah an zirh vivo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kawhhran umnak poh ah kawhhran upa an ret vivo ih thlacam le rawl-ul in an rinsanmi an Bawipa hnenah hlannak an tuahta vivo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Pisidia ram an lan ṭheh hnuah Pamfilia ram an thleng.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Thuthang ṭha Perga khua ah an sim ih cuih hnuah Attalia khua ah an vung feh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cutawk ihsin lawng in Antiok khua ah an kir. Antiok khua cu atu-ih an ṭhehmi an hnaṭuan ṭuan dingah Pathian hnenih an rak pek awknak khua kha a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Antiok khua an thlen tikah kawhhran senpi pawl an kokhawm ih Pathian in anmah a hmanzia le Zentail mi pawl Pathian thu zum dingih lamzin a on sakzia pawl an sim.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cutawkah zumtu pawl thawn reipi an um tlang."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Mi ṭhenkhat Judea ram ihsin Antiok khua ah an ra ih, “Moses Daan ih in fial bangtuk in serh nan tan lo ahcun rundamnak nan ngah thei lo ding,” tiah zumtu unau pawl an zirh ciamco.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih thu cu Paul le Barnabas in nasa zetin an el; cule a netnak ah hi thu-ah hin tirhthlah pawl le kawhhran upa pawl thawn Jerusalem ih vung tong aw dingin Paul le Barnabas le Antiok khua ih upa dang pawl an fial.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> An feh zawng ah kawhhran pawl in an thlah. Cule Fawnisia le Samaria ram an pal phah ih cutawkah Zentail mi pawl ziang bangtuk in Pathian lamah an lung an thleng zo ti kha an theihter phah vivo. Cuih thu an theih tikah zumtu pawl cu an lung a awi ngaingai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Jerusalem an thlen tikah kawhhran le tirhthlah pawl le kawhhran upa pawl in an rak hmuak ih a rak hmuaktu pawl hnenah cun Pathian ih hnaṭuannak kha kimtein an sim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sikhalsehla Farasi pawl sungih a telmi zumtu hrekkhat pawl cun, “Zentail mi pawl cu serh an tan hrimhrim a ṭul ih Moses Daan thlun dingin kan sim a ṭul a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Curuangah tirhthlah pawl le kawhhran upa pawl cu cuih thu ruat dingah an tong aw khawm.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Caan reipi an el awk hnuah Piter a ding ih, “Ka u le ka nau tla, nan theih zo vekin kei hi nanmah lak ihsin Zentail mi pawl in Thuthang ṭha an theih ih an zum thei venak dingah Thuthang ṭha an hnenih sim dingah Pathian in i hrilnak a rei zo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule mi hmuahhmuah ih ruahnak a thei ṭhehtu Pathian in Zentail mi pawl khal a pom a si; cuih a pomnak cu kan hnenih Thlarau Thianghlim in pek vekin an hnen khalah Thlarau Thianghlim a peknak in a langter zo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Pathian in anmah le kanmah karlakah thleidannak zianghman a nei lo; an zum ruangah an sualnak khal a ngaidam a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuti a si ruangah ziangah so kan pu le kan pa pawl in siseh, kanmah khal in siseh kan phurh thei lomi thilrit cu zumtu pawl ih zaang parah suang tahratin Pathian cu hniksak nan duh?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Asilo! Kannih hi anmah vek thotho in zumnak kan nei ih Bawipa Jesuh ih zaangfah thinpemnak thawngin rundamnak kan ngah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Paul le Barnabas khal in Pathian in anmah hmangin Zentail mi lakah hmuhsaknak mak le khawruahhar a phunphun a tuahmi hmuahhmuah kha an sim tikah an zatein dai khepkhep in an ngai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> An sim ṭheh tikah Jeim a ding ih, “Ka u le ka nau tla, i ngaihnik uh!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Simon in atute ih a ṭong zomi cu nan thei. Zentail mi pawl khal Pathian in an zawn a ruat ih anmah lak ihsin minung hrekkhat cu Amah ih ta si dingah a hril a si, tiah a simfiang zo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Profet pawl khal in hivek thothoin an rak sim zo. Ca Thianghlim in:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ‘Bawipa in, himi hnuah, Ka ra kir sal ding ih A tlu zomi David ih uknak cu ka tung sal ding. A siatbal mi cu ka sak ding ih ka cakter sal ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cuti cun leilung tlun miphun hmuahhmuah ka hnenah an ra ding; Ka hril ciami Zentail mi hmuahhmuah khal an ra ding.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Khuahlan lai ihsin hi thu a theitertu Bawipa in a ti,’ tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Curuangah kei ka ruahnak ahcun: Pathian a pantu Zentail mi pawl hi hnaihnawhnak pe hlah uhsi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cuhnakin an hnenah milem biaknak rawl thiang lo ei lo dingin le nupa sualnak tuah lo dingin le hngawngrek-ih thahmi sa le sathi pohpoh ei lo dingin ca kuat sawn uhsi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ziangahtile Sabbath tinte in sinakok ah Moses Daan cu kum reipi sung siar a si zo ih Pathian thu khal khawkip ah sim a si zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule tirhthlah pawl, kawhhran upa pawl le kawhhran zate in anmah sung ihsin mi ṭhenkhat hril tahratin Paul le Barnabas thawn Antiok khua ih thlah dingah an rel. Anmah lakah zumtu pawl in an upat zetmi pahnih, Barsabbas ti khal in an kawhmi Judas le Silas an hril ih,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> a tanglamih ca kuat hi an kut ah an pek: “Nan unau a si mi kannih tirhthlah pawl le kawhhran upa pawl in Antiok le Siria le Silisia ih a ummi Zentail unau pawl nan zate hnenah cibai kan lo buk.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hitawkih kan pawl sung ihsin nan hnen a ra thlengmi ṭhenkhat in an ṭongkam in harsatnak an lo pek ih an lo buaiter ti kan thei. Hitiih an ra ṭong tikah kannih ih kan fialmi an si lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Curuangah kan tong-aw khawm ih kanmah sung ihsin hrilmi palai nan hnenah kan hun thlah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kan Bawipa Jesuh Khrih hnaṭuannak hrangah nunnak tiangin a pe ngamtu kan duhdawtmi Paul le Barnabas thawn an hung ding.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cuti cun Judas le Silas nan hnenah kan hun thlah ih anmah in hi ca sungih kan nganmi hi an lo sim ding.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Thlarau Thianghlim le kannih lungkim tlangnak kan nei ih hi a tanglam ih a ṭulmi daan pawl siarlo a dang thilrit nan parih ret ding kan duh lo:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Milem biaknak rawl nan ei lo pei; sathi nan ei lo pei; hngawngrek-ih thahmi sa nan ei lo pei; cule nupa sualnak nan tuah lo pei. Himi pawl tuah loin nan hrial thei a si ahcun a ṭha thluh ding. Damte in um hram uh,” tiah an ngan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> An thlahmi an palai pawl cu an feh ih Antiok an thleng. Cutawkih zumtu pawl hmuahhmuah cu an ko khawm ih an kenmi cakuat cu an pek.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cumi an siar tikah mipi thapeknak ca a si ruangah an lung a awi ngaingai.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Judas le Silas anmah khal cu profet an si ih mipi hnenah ralṭhatnak le thacahnak thu reipi an sim.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cutawkih tawkfang an um hnuah zumtu pawl in hnangamte in an thlah ih anmah a hun thlahtu kawhhran hnenah an kir sal.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> (Sikhalsehla Silas cu cunah a taangta.)",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Paul le Barnabas cu tawkfang sung Antiok ah an um ih midang tampi thawn Pathian thu an zirh ih an sim.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Malte a rei deuh hnuah Paul in, “Bawipa ih thu kan rak simnak ah khan feh sal uhsila khawkip ih unau pawl kan va tlawng sal pei ih an umtlandan kan va zoh sal pei,” tiah Barnabas cu a ti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Barnabas in Johan Marka kha an hnenah fehter a duh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Asinain Paul in Johan Marka hruai ding cu a ṭha tiin a ruat lo, ziangahtile Johan Marka cun an khualtlawnnak a net tiang thlun loin Pamfilia ihsin a kirsan hai ruangah a si.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Cuih thu-ah cun Paul le Barnabas cu napi-in an el aw ih an ṭhen aw. Barnabas in Marka cu a hruai ih Saipras ah lawng in an feh.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Paul in Silas a hruai ih zumtu pawl in Bawipa ih zaangfahnak thawn va feh hram uhlaw tiah an thlahta.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Paul le Silas cu Siria ram le Silisia ram sung an pal phah ih kawhhran pawl kha tha an pek phah vivo."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Paul cu Derbe khua le Listra khua a va thleng; cutawkah dungthlun a si mi Timote a um. A nu cu Judah mi a si ih Khristian a si ve, a pa cu Grik mi a si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Listra khua le Ikoniam khua ih a ummi zumtu pawl in Timote cu an porhzet.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Paul in Timote cu hruai a duh ruangah a serh a tanter. Ziangahtile cutawk khawsungih a ummi Judah mi pawl in Timote ih pa cu Grik mi a si ti kha an theih ṭheh ruangah a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Khua pakhat hnu pakhat an thleng vivo ih Jerusalem khua ih tirhthlah pawl le kawhhran upa pawl in an relcatmi daan pawl kha zumtu pawl hnenah an sim vivo ih thlun ding khalah an forh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Curuangah kawhhran pawl cu zumnak lamah an cak deuhdeuh ih ni khat hnu ni khat minung an tam sinsin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Asia ram sungih Thuthang ṭha sim dingah Thlarau Thianghlim in a on lo ruangah Frizia le Kalatia ram sungah khual an tlawng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Misia ramri an thleng ih Bithinia ramsung luh an tum, asinain Jesuh ih Thlarau in a on lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Curuangah Misia ram cu an lan ih Troas khua ah an feh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih zanah Paul in langnak a hmu ih cuih a hmuhmi ahcun Masidonia mi pakhat ding tahratin, “Masidonia ah ra awla in ra bawm aw,” tiah zaangfah a dil.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Paul ih langnak a hmuh ṭheh vete in Masidonia ih feh dingah kan tim kan tuah, ziangahtile cutawk mi pawl hnenih Thuthang ṭha sim dingah Pathian in in ko a si tiah kan zum.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Troas ihsin lawng in kan feh ih Samothrace ah dingtein kan feh; cule a thaisun ah Neapolis kan thleng.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutawk ihsin leilung in Filipi khua kan thleng. Filipi khua cu Masidonia ram sungih peng pakhatnak ih khawpi a si. Rom ih ukmi khua a si fawn. Cutawkah ni tampi kan caam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sabbath ni ah khawpi ihsin tivakap ah kan feh; cutawkah Judah mi pawl hmun khatih thlacamnak hmun a um ding tiah kan ruat. Kan to ih cutawkih a rami nunau pawl thawn, thu kan ruah aw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> An lakih pakhat, kan thu a ngaitu cu Thiatira khuami Lydia a si ih amah cu puan sendup zuartu a si. Amah cu Pathian a biatu a si ih Paul thusimmi kha ṭhateih ngai dingah Bawipa in Lydia ih thinlung sangka a on.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Amah le a innsungsang pawl baptisma an lak ṭheh hnuah, Lydia in, “Bawipa a zum taktak tiih in ruat asile ka inn ah ra caam ve hram uh!” tiah in sawm. Cutiin in sawm suak ih kan va feh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ni khatah thlacamnak hmunih kan feh laiah, khawsia polhmi hmailam thu a simsung theitu sal nunau pakhat in in rak hmuak. Hmailam thu a simsungnak in a bawi pawl hrangah tangka tampi a ngah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Paul le kanmah cu in thlun vivo ih, “Himi pawl hi Cungnungbik Pathian ih sal an si! Rundamnak thu nan hnenah an phuang a si!” tiah a au vivo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuti cun ni tampi sung a tuah ih a netnak ah Paul cu a thin-ai a thok ih a dunglet hoi tahratin a khawsia hnenah cun, “Hi nu sung ihsin suak dingah Jesuh ih hmin in thu ka lo pek!” tiah a ti. Hmakhatteah a khawsia cu a suak.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Amah a neitu pawl in tangka an ngah theinak lamzin a um nawn lo ti kha an theih tikah Paul le Silas cu an kaih ih thuneitu bawi pawl hnenah miburpi tonkhawmnak hmunah an dirh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Rom Acozah bawi thuṭhentu pawl hmaiah an hruai ih, “Himi pawl hi Judah mi phun an si ih kan khawsungah buainak an suahter.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kan daan thawn a kaih-aw lomi daan an zirh; kannih cu Rom Acozah minung kan si ih hi an zirhmi daan hi kan pom thei lo, a thlun khal kan thlun lo,” tiah an ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule misenpi pawl khal Paul le Silas a huatu ah an tel ve. Cuih hnuah Acozah bawi thuṭhentu pawl in Paul le Silas ih hnipuan cu an dirhthleksak ih vuak dingah thu an pek.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Besiazet ih an vuak hnuah thawng sungah an khum ih thawnginn uktu pa cu ṭhateih tawh hren dingin thu an pek.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cuih thupekmi a ngah vekin thawnginn uktu pa in Paul le Silas cu thawnginn sungta khaan sungah a vun khum ih a rit zetmi thingtum pahnih in hreng a sut.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Zanṭim hrawngah Paul le Silas cu thla an cam ih Pathian thangṭhatnak hla an sak; cule thawngtla dang pawl in an rak ngai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Rinlopi-ah nasa zetin ling a hnin ih thawnginn cu a tawhram tiangin a hnin ṭheh. Hmakhatte-ah sangka pawl an ong aw ṭheh ih thawngtla pawl hmuahhmuah ih kut khihnak thir cikcin cu an phoih aw ṭheh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Thawnginn uktu cu a ṭhang ih thawnginn sangka pawl a ong ṭheh ti a hmuh tikah thawngtla pawl an tlan thluh zo tiin a ruat ih, a ralnam zuuk tahratin amah le amah thah awk a tum.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul cu a aw neih patawp in a au ih, “Nangmah le nangmah tuahmawh aw hlah! Kan zatein kan um thluh ko,” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Thawnginn kiltu pa cun meisa rak keng uh, a ti ih thawnginn sungah zamrangin a lut ih khur phah rero in Paul le Silas kehram ah a bok.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cule lengah a hruai hai ih, “Ka bawipale pawl, rundamnak ngah dingah ziangso ka tuah ding?” tiah a sut.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Annih in, “Bawi Jesuh zum awla nangmah le nan sungte in rundamnak nan ngah ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Cule Pathian thu cu amah le a innsang zate hnenah an sim.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cuih zan rori-ah cun thawnginn uktu pa in a fehpi hai ih an hmaa pawl cu a buah sak; cule cuvete in amah le a innsang zatein baptisma an lak.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Cun Paul le Silas cu a inn ah a hruai ih rawl ei ding a pek. Amah le a innsang zatein Pathian an zum ngah ruangah lungawinak in an khat.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> A thaizing ah Rom Acozah bawi thuṭhentu pawl in palik bawi pawl an hei thlah ih, “Kha pawl kha thlah hai uh,” tiah thu an pek.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Curuangah thawnginn uktu pa in Paul cu, “Thuṭhentu bawi pawl in nangmah le Silas thlah dingin thu an rak pe. Curuangah suak uhla, daitein feh uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul in palik bawi pawl hnenah cun, “Sualnak zianghman kan nei lo naón mizapi hmai rori-ah in thawi; Rom Acozah minung kan si ve! Cuih tlunah thawngah in thlak. Cule atu-ah a thupte in fehter in tum maw si? Feh naisai hlah! Rom Acozah bawi pawl anmah rori hinah ra hai sehla in ra suah hai seh!” tiah a ti.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cutiih a timi cu palik bawi pawl in Rom Acozah bawi thuṭhentu pawl hnenah an va sim; cule Paul le Silas cu Rom mi an si ti an theih tikah an thin a phang!",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Curuangah Paul le Silas hnenah cun an va feh ih ngaithiamnak an va dil; cule thawnginn ihsin an suah ih khawsung ihsin hmun dangah feh uh, tiin an dil.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Paul le Silas cu thawnginn ihsin an suak ih Lydia ih inn ah an feh. Cutawkah zumtu unau pawl an tong ih thazaang peknak thu an sim hnuah cuih khua ihsin an suak."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Paul le Silas cu Amfipolis le Appollonia an tlawng ih Thesalonika khua an thleng. Cutawkah Judah mi pawl ih sinakok a um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amah ih tuah keel vekin Paul cu Sinakok ah a feh. Cutawkah Sabbath ni ni thum sung rori mipi thawn thu an el aw ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Messiah cu thihnak a tuar ding ih a thosal ding a si ti kha Ca Thianghlim sung ihsin a langter ih a simfiang vivo. “Nan hnenih ka phuanmi Jesuh hi Messiah cu a si,” tiah Paul in a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mi ṭhenkhat cu an thinlung a fiang ngah ih Paul le Silas kha an kom. Cuvekin nunau hotu pawl le Pathian a biatu Grik mi tampi a burpi in Paul le Silas hnenah an kom ve.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sikhalsehla Judah mi pawl in an nahsiik ih lamzin ih a vak lakmi mi hlothlau ṭhenkhat pawl kha an khawm ih miburpi ah an cang. Khawsungah an au an kio ih nasa zetin buainak an suahpi. Jason an timi pa ih inn an va kulh ih cutawkah Paul le Silas kha kai ih mipi hmai ah hnuk an tum.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sikhalsehla cutawk inn ah Paul le Silas cu an hmu lo ih Jason le zumtu ṭhenkhat pawl sawn kha khawsung upa hmaiah an hruai ih, “Hmunzakipah buainak a suahtertu pawl, atu-ah kan khawsung an ra thleng ih,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Jason in a inn sungah a umter hai. An ṭongmi cu ‘Jesuh timi siangpahrang dang pakhat a um,’ an tiih cuti cun Rom siangpahrang ih daan an buar a si,” tiah an au ciamco.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutiih an aunak ruangah miburpi le khawsung upa pawl cu an buaiter ṭheh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Thuneitu pawl in Jason le a rualpi pawl cu anmah thlah dingih a ṭul zat tangka an lak ih cuih hnuah an thlah sal.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Khua a thim vete in zumtu pawl in Paul le Silas cu Berea khua ah an thlah. Berea khua an thlen tikah sinakok ah an feh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutawkih mipi pawl cu Thesalonika mi pawl hnakin an thinlung a tluangtlam deuh. An thusimmi pawl cu an thinlung taktein an ngai ih, nitinte in Paul ih simmi cu a si ngaingai maw, si ngaingai lo tiah Ca Thianghlim an siar ih an zohṭhim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Mi tampi in an zum; upat tlak Grik nunau pawl le Grik mipa pawl khal in an zum ve.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Asinain Thesalonika ih ummi Judah mi pawl in Berea khua khalah Paul in Pathian thu a sim ti an theih tikah Berea khua ahcun an ra ih mipi kha an tokhrok ih an buaiter ciamco.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hmakhatte-ah zumtu pawl in Paul cu tifinriat lamah an tlanter; asinain Silas le Timote cu Berea ah an taangta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Paul a thlahtu zumtu pawl in Paul cu Athens khua tiang an thlun; cule a thluntu pawl cu an kir ih Silas le Timote in a zamrang thei tawkih amah hei dawi dingah Paul in thu a cah hai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Paul in Silas le Timote kha Athens khua ihsin a hngak laiah cuih khawpi cu milem zuk in a khat ti kha a hmu ih a thin a nau ngaingai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Curuangah Judah mi pawl le Pathian a biatu Grik mi pawl thawn an pumkhawmnak inn sinakok ah thu an el aw ṭheu; mizapi ton awknak hmun khalah a rami pawl thawn an el aw ringring.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Epikurian thuzirhtu saya ṭhenkhat le Stoik thuzirhtu saya hrekkhat pawl thawn khal thu an el aw. Mi hrekkhat in, “Zianghman thei sii lo, hi pa hin mi hmaiah lang duh zetin ziangso rel a tum rero?” tiah an ti. Mihrek in, “Ramdang pathian pawl ih thuhla a sim a bang,” an ti. Ziangah cutin an ti tile Paul in Jesuh le a thawhsalnak thu a sim ruangah a si.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Curuangah Paul cu Areopagas an timi an khua ih khonsil hnenah an suahpi ih, “Thuthar na zirhmi hi ziangso a si, ti kan thei duh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A hrekkhat na simmi kan theihmi cu a lamdang zet ih a tican ziang a si ti kan thei duh,” tiah an ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> (Ziangah cutin an ti tile Athens khua mi hmuahhmuah le hi khua ih a ummi ramdang mi tla cu thu thar le thil thar kha an tikcu zate hmangin theih rero le sim rero a duh bikmi pawl an si.)",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Paul cu an khua khonsil Areopagas timi upa hmaiah cun a ding ih an hnenah, “Nannih Athens mi pawl hi biaknak lam pohpoh ahcun nan taimazet ti ka hmu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ziangahtile nan khawpi sungih ka toihvah tikah Pathian nan biaknak hmun pawl tla ka zoh ih biakṭheng pakhat parah ‘Kan Theih Lomi Pathian Hnenah,’ tiih nan nganmi ka hmu. Cutiin nan thei lo na-cingih nan biakmi Pathian cu atu nan hnenih ka phuanmi hi a si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Leilung le a sungih a ummi hmuahhmuah a tuahtu Pathian cu lei le vanih Bawi a si ih milai kutih sakmi biakinn sungah a um lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cuih tlunah Pathian cu mi hmuahhmuah hnenah nunnak le thaw le thildang hmuahhmuah a petu Pathian a si ruangah milai in a hrangih kan tuahmi kha a ṭulmi zianghman a um lo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Minung pakhat sung ihsin leilung miphun hmuahhmuah a tuah ih leilung pumpuluk ah a umter ṭheh. A hlankhan in ziangtik caanah an um ding ih khuitawk hmun tiang an um thei ding, ti kha a relcia ṭheh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangah hiti in a tawlrel cia tile Pathian an hawl ih an hmuh suak theinak dingah a si. Sikhalsehla a ngaingai ti-ah cun Pathian cu zo thawn hman a hlat lo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mi pakhat ih a rak sim cia vekin, ‘Amah ih sungah kan nung, kan tlangleng ih khua kan sa!’ tiah nan hla phuahtu ṭhenkhat pawl ih an tivek in, ‘Kannih khal hi a faate kan si ve.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cutiih Pathian ih faate kan si ruangah thilthiam pawl le zuk suaithiam pawl in sui milem le ngun milem le lungto milem an tuahmi hi Pathian ah kan ruah ding a si hrimhrim lo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Minung in Pathian thei lo bembem ih an rak um caan kha cu Amah Pathian in hmu lo vekin a um san meen; sikhalsehla atu-ah cun an nuncan ṭha lomi ihsin sualsir dingah mi hmuahhmuah kha a fial a si.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ziangahtile a hril ciami mi pakhat in leilung pumpuluk hi dingnak thawn thuṭhen cat dingah ni a tin zo. Cuih thu cu thudik a si, ti kha mi hmuahhmuah hnenah langternak ah cupa cu thihnak ihsin a thoter sal zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Mithi thawhsalnak thu Paul ih a simmi an theih tikah mi hrek in an hnihsan; asinain midang in, “In sim sal hrih cila kan duh,” tiah an ti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cuih hnuah Paul cu an khawmnak ihsin a feh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Mi hrekkhat in an thlun ih an zum. A zumtu lakah cun Khonsil upa Dionisias tla a tel. Damaris an timi nunau pakhat le midang ṭhenkhat khal an tel."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah Paul cu Athens ihsin a feh ih Korin khua a thleng.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutawkah Pontus ramih a suakmi Judah mi Aquila a tong. Aquila cu a nupi Prisilla thawn Italy ihsin a ra tlanmi an si. Ziangahtile Rom siangpahrang Klaudius in Judah mi hmuahhmuah cu Rom khua ihsin a dawi ruangah an tlan. Paul cun a va tong hai ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> an hnenah a caam ih anmah thawn hna a ṭuan. Aquila le Prisilla cu puanthlam tuah in pumcawmmi an si ih anmah vekin Paul khal puanthlam tuah in a pum a cawm aw ve.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sabbath nitinte in sinakok ah Judah mi le Grik mi pawl an thinlung fiangter dingah thu an ruah aw, an el aw ṭheu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Masidonia ihsin Silas le Timote an ra thlen tikah Paul cu a tikcu neihmi hmuahhmuah in Pathian thusimnak ah a hmang ih Jesuh cu Messiah taktak a si tiah Judah mi hnenah a sim ciamco.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Annih in Paul cu an engtai ih ṭong siava tla in an leh tikah Paul in a lungkimlonak langternak ah a hnipuan ih leivut kha a thinta ih, “Nan hloral a si ahcun nanmah ih mawh a si ding! Kei i mawhthluk hlah uh! Atu ihsin Zentail mi hnenah ka feh ding!” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Curuangah a feh ih Zentail mi Titias Jastas an timi pa inn ah a um; Titias Jastas cu Pathian a biatu a si ih a inn cu sinakok kiangte ah a um.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sinakok uktu upa bik Krispas khal a sungkhat pawl thawn Bawipa an zum; cule Korin khuami tampi tla in Pathian thu cu an thei ih an zum ruangah baptisma an lak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Zankhat ah Paul in langnak a hmu ih cuih sung ihsin Bawipa in, “Paul, ṭih hlah! Sim rero ko aw, na bei dong hlah!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na hnenah ka um a si. Zohman in harnak an lo pe thei lo ding, ziangahtile hi khawsungih mi tampi cu ka minung an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Curuangah Paul cu kum khat le a hrek sung a um ih mipi hnenah Pathian thu a zirh ringring.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Gallio in Akhaia ram uktu Rom Mangki a ṭuan laiah Judah mi pawl an tongkhawm aw ih Paul cu an kai ih zungah an suahpi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “Hi pa hin mi tampi hnenah kan daan thawn a kaih aw lomi Pathian biak daan a zirh a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Paul a hung ṭong zik zawng ah Gallio in Judah mi hnenah, “Thil ṭha lo le thil sual pakhatkhat tuah ruangah a si ahcun Judah mi pawl nan parah thinlung sau zetin ka um ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sikhalsehla atu cu nan biaknak ih ṭong fang le hmin le nan daan ruangih thu el aw nan si ruangah nanmah tein va relcat uh! Cubangtuk thu-ah cun thuṭhentu ka si thei lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule a zung ihsin Judah mi pawl cu a dawi ṭheh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sinakok inn uktu Sosthenes kha an zatein an kai ih zung hmai rori ah an vuak. Asinain Gallio cun zianghman ah a siarsak lo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Paul cu Korin khua ih zumtu pawl thawn ni tampi sung an um hnuah Prisilla le Aquila thawn lawng in Siria ah an feh. Kenkhria ihsin lawng in an feh hlanah thu tiamkamnak a rak tuah zo bangtuk in Paul cu a lu a meet.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Efesa khua an thleng ih cutawk ah Prisilla le Aquila cu a taan. Sinakok ah a lut ih Judah mi pawl thawn thu an ruah aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Rei deuh um dingin an sawm naón a lung a kim lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A feh zawng ah thu a cahta ih, “Pathian lungkimnak a si ahcun nan hnenah ka ra sal leh ding,” tiah a ti. Cule Efesa ihsin lawng in a feh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sisaria a thlen tikah Jerusalem khua ah a lan ih cutawkih kawhhran kha a tongta ih Antiok ah a hung feh sal.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cutawkah tawkfang sung a um hnuah a pok sal ih Kalatia le Frizia ram a tlawng ih zumtu hmuahhmuah an thazaang a cakter.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Culai ah Alexandria khua ih suak, Apollos timi Judah pa cu Efesa khua ah a ra thleng. Amah cu ṭong a thiam zet ih Ca Thianghlim tla a thei ngaingaimi a si.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bawipa ih Lamzin thuhla ah zirh zomi a si ih, thinlung thozet le felzetin Jesuh ih thuhla cu a sim ih a zirh. Asinain a theihmi cu Johan ih baptisma thu lawnglawng a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ralṭha zetin sinakok ah thu a sim. A thusimmi cu Prisilla le Aquila in an theih tikah an inn ah an sawm ih Pathian Lamzin thuhla kha felfai deuh in an sim.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cule Apollos cu Akhaia peng ih feh a tum ruangah Efesa khua ih zumtu pawl in an bawm ih Akhaia khua ih dungthluntu pawl hnenah Apollos an rak mikhual theinak dingah ca an ngansak. Akhaia khua a thlen tikah Pathian zaangfahnak thawngin zumtu a rak si mi pawl hrangah bawmtu ṭhazet ah a cang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ziangahtile mi thu el a thiamzet ih Jesuh cu Messiah taktak a si, tiah Ca Thianghlim sung ihsin la tahrat in a fiangter ih cuticun zapi hmaiih thu el awknak ah Judah mi pawl kha a neh thei ringring."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Apollos cu Korin khua ih a um laiah Paul cu cuih ram sungah khual a tlawng ih Efesa ah a thleng. Cutawkah dungthluntu ṭhenkhat pawl a tong ih,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Paul in, “Zumtu nan si zo ih Thlarau Thianghlim nan ngah maw?” tiah a sut. Annih in, “Thlarau Thianghlim a um ti hman kan theih ual lo,” tiah an sawn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Cuti asile ziangvek baptisma so nan lak?” tiah Paul in a sut. Annih in, “Johan ih baptisma,” tiah an ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutikah Paul in, “Johan ih baptisma cu sual a sir awmi pawl hrangah a si ih amah Johan in ka dungih a ra ding pa kha Israel mi pawl in an zum dingmi a si. Cumi cu Jesuh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cumi an theih tikah Bawi Jesuh hmin in baptisma an lak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Paul in an parah a kut a suang ih an parah Thlarau Thianghlim a rung thleng; ṭong phun dangdang in an ṭong ih Pathian thu cu profet bangin an phuang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Anmah cu pacang hlir hleihnih tluk an si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Paul cu sinakok ah a feh ih thla thum sung ralṭha zetin mipi hnenah thu a sim. Anmah thawn thu an el aw ih Pathian Uknak thu kha an thinlung ah lut ngah dingin a zuam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sikhalsehla mi ṭhenkhat cu an thinlung a ruhzet ih an zum duh lo; curuangah miburpi hmaiah Bawipa ih Lamzin thuhla kha an relsiat ciamco. Curuangah Paul in a tlansan ih zumtu pawl kha a fehpi ih Tirannas timi thusimnak innpi ah nitinte in thu a zirh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cuti cun kum hnih sung a ṭuan ih Asia ram sungih a ummi Judah mi siseh, Zentail mi siseh, an zatein Bawipa ih thu cu an thei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Pathian in Paul kha a hmang ih lamdang zet, mangbangza pawl a tuah.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A pavua le a taaingerh puan pawl hman kha mina pawl hnenah an ken tikah an natnak a dam ih an sung ihsin khuasia pawl an suak.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hmunkipah vak tahratih khuasia a dawitu Judah mi ṭhenkhat tla in Bawi Jesuh hmin in Paul vekih tuah ve an tum. Annih in khuasia pawl hnenah, “Paul ih a simmi Jesuh ih hmin in ka lo dawi,” tiah an ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Judah mi Puithiam Saang a hmin Skeva an timi pa ih fapa unau pasarih in cubangtuk cun an tuah ciamco.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sikhalsehla khawsia in an hnenah cun, “Jesuh ka thei; Paul thuhla khal ka thei. Sikhalsehla nannih hi zoso nan si?” tiah a ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Khuasia polhmi pa cun unau pasarih pawl cu a zon ih a sual hai ih a neh thluh. Hmapu le hnipuan tlek ṭheh-in a inn ihsin an tlan.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cuih thuhla cu Efesa khua ih a ummi Judah mi le Zentail mi hmuahhmuah in an theih tikah an ṭih ngaingai ih Jesuh hmin cu upatnak an pek sinsin.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zumtu sung ihsin mi tampi an ra ih zapi hmaiah thil an rak tuah ṭheumi pawl kha an phuang ciamco.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mitkherh thiam tampi tla in an mitkher cabu pawl cu hmun khatah an khawm ih zapi mithmuh ah an ur. Cutiih an urmi mitkher cabu pawl cu a man an kom tikah ngun tangka thawng sawmnga a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cuti cun Bawipa ih thu cu nasa zetin a zai ih a cak sinsin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cubangtuk in thil a um hnuah Paul in Masidonia ram le Akhaia ram hrawng tlawn ih Jerusalem ih lanta ding kha a thinlung in a ruat. “Cutawk ka thlen hnuah Rom khal ka hmuh a ṭul,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Curuangah amah a bawmtu lakih pahnih Timote le Erastas kha Masidonia ah a thlah ih amah cu Asia ram sungah tikcu tam deuh a hmang.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cuih tikcu hrawngah Efesa khua ah Bawipa ih Lamzin thuhla ah thubuai tumpi pakhat a um.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngun in sosertu Demetrias an timi pa in khawzingnu Artemis ih biakinn zuk kha ngun in a ser ih a hnaṭuantu pawl hrangah tangka tampi a ngah.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Curuangah a hnaṭuantu pawl le anmah vekih hnaṭuantu dangdang pawl kha a kokhawm ih an hnenah, “U le nau pawl, hi kan hnaṭuanmi ruangah hin neinungin kan um ti cu nan theih ṭhehmi a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asinain atu-ah Paul an timi pa in ziang bangtuk in hna a ṭuan ti cu nanmah rori-in nan hmuhmi le nan theihmi a si. ‘Milai ih tuahcopmi pathian cu pathian an si lo,’ tiah a ti ih Efesa khawsung le Asia ram zate ti ding tlak in mi tampi thinlung ah a simmi cu a lut ngah a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cuti a si ruangah hi kan hnaṭuanmi hi a hmin a sia thlang ding tihi phan a umzet. Cuih tlunah Asia ram le leilung tlun pumpuluk ah mikip miza in an biakmi a ropi zetmi khawzingnu Artemis ih biakinn hi mi in zianghman ah an siar nawn lo ding ih a ropitnak hi a cemralta ding a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cumi cu mipi in an theih tikah an thin a hengzet ih, “Efesa khua ih Artemis cu a ropi a si,” tiah an au ciamco.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cutiih an au cu khawsungah a khat ṭheh. Mipi cun, Masidonia mi pahnih Paul thawn khual a tlawng tlangmi Kaias le Aristarkas kha an kai ih puai zohnak bualrawn ah an suahpi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mipi hmaiah cun Paul amah rori suah a duh naón zumtu pawl in an kham.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cuih peng sungih thuneitu a rualpi pawl hrekkhat in cuih bualrawn ih va feh hrimhrim lo dingin thu an cah fawn.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Cutiin bualrawn ahcun an buai rero; mihrek in pakhat thu an au, midang in thudang thu an rak au ve; mi tam sawn cun cutawkah ziangah kan ra suak ti hman an thei lo.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Judah mi pawl in Alexander kha hmaiih an suahter ruangah mi tampi cun hi thubuai a suahtertu hi amah a si hmang tiah an ruat. Cule Alexander cun dai uh, tiah a kut in mipi cu a hun hmuh hai ih amah ih dinhmun ṭan in thusim a tum.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sikhalsehla Judah mi a si kha mipi in an theih tikah an au keel in an au hluarhlo sal ih, “Efesa khua ih Artemis cu a ropi a si,” tiah nazi pahnih sung an au.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> A netnak ah cuih khua ih thuneitu lakih sungṭuantu pa in mipi cu a daihter deuh ih an hnenah cun, “Efesa khuami pawl, Efesa khua cu a ropimi Artemis ih biakinn le vancung ihsin a rung tlami milem umnak hmun a si ti cu mi hmuahhmuahih theih ṭhehmi a si.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> A el theitu zoso a um? Zohman in an el thei lo ding. Curuangah daitein um uhla ruatta ciamciam loin zianghman tuah hlah uh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Himi pawl hin biakinn sung thilri an ruk lo, kan khuavangnu khal an relsiat lo naón hinah nan rak suahpi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Demetrias le a hnaṭuantu pawl in zo ih tlun khalah sual mawhthluk ding an neih a si ahcun tazacuai theinak zung kan nei ko; thuṭhen ni le thuṭhentu upa tla kan nei ko. Cunah thukhiin theih a si.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Cuhnakih thupi deuh nan duh asile kan daan vekin khawsungmi zate ih pumkhawmnak ah relcat ding a si.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ziangahtile tuihsun ih thil a cangmi ruangah hin buainak nan suahpi tiin mawhthluk kan tong pang ding ti phan a um. Hi tluk lawmmam ih buainak thu-ah hin puhmawh ding a um lo; cule ziangah nan buai tiah in ti hai sehla ṭan kan la thei lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Cutiih a ti hnuah a ra khawmmi pawl cu a ṭiakter hai."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih thubuai cu a dai ih Paul in a zumtu pawl cu hmun khatah a kokhawm ih thapeknak ṭongkam in a forh hnuah cibai a bukta hai ih Masidonia ramah a feh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cuih ram cu a tlawng vivo ih thapeknak thu a sim vivo. Cule Akhaia a thleng ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> cutawkah thla thum a caam. Siria ah feh a tum naón, a tim a tuah rero laiah Judah mi pawl ih an zuar tum thu a theih ruangah Masidonia lam in feh sal a tum.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Berea khuami Pirhas ih fapa Sopater le Thesalonika khuami Aristarkas le Sekundas, Derbe khuami Kaias, Asia ram in Taikhikas le Trofimas, le Timote tla in Paul cu an fehpi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> An rak feh sungih Troas ihsin in rak hngak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Thilnu tello Sang Puai a cem hnuah Filipi ihsin lawng in kan feh ih ni nga hnuah Troas ah kan man hai. Troas ahcun zarh khat kan caam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Zarhte ni zanlam ah pawlkomnak zanriah hil tlang dingin kan tongkhawm aw. A ra khawmmi hnenah Paul in thu a sim ih a thaizing feh ding a si ruangah zanṭim tiang thu a sim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tlunta khaan ah kan khawm aw ih mei-inn tampi an vang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Tlangval pakhat Zutikhas an timi cu saangkate ah a to ih Paul in reipi thu a sim tikah cun a ih a rak hmu deuhdeuh ih a netnak ahcun a ihthat ngah ruangah cuih inn dot thumnak ihsin leilung ah a tla. An vung sar tikah a rak thi zo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul a vung ṭum ih cuih tlangvalpa cu a bawhhnawh ih a pom. Paul in, “Nan thinphang hlah uh, a nunglai a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule Paul cu tlunta khaanah cun a hung kai sal ih sang kha a phel ih an ei. Paul cu reipi, zinglam nisuak tiang thu a sim hnuah a feh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuih tlangvalpa cu a nungin a inn ah an fehpi ih an hna a ngam zet.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lawng parah kan va feh ih cuih lawng in Assos ah kan feh; Assos ahcun Paul sawm phah ding kan si. Cutiih sawm phah ding cu in sim ciami a si, ziangahtile lei lamzin in anih cu a rak feh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Assos ah Paul cu kan tong ih kan lawng parah kan toter ih Mitilene ah kan feh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mitilene ihsin kan suak ih a thaisun ah Khios zawn kan thleng. A tipsun ah Samos kan thleng ih a thiamsun ah Miletas kan thleng.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Paul cun Asia ramih caam rei ding cu a duh lo ruangah Efesa lansan mai a tum. A cang thei a si ahcun Pentikos ni kheel in Jerusalem ih thlen lohli a duh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Paul in Miletas ihsin mi a thlah ih Efesa khua kawhhran upa pawl in amah rak tong dingin thu a cah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An rat tikah Paul cun, “Asia ram ka ra thlen ih a ni khatnak ni ihsin ka tikcu hmuahhmuah cu nan hnenah ziangvekin ka hmang ti cu nan thei ṭheh ko.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Tangdornak le mitthli thawn Bawipa ka rian ih Judah mi pawl ih in phiarnak khal har fualfo-in ka tuar.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Zapi hmaiah siseh, nan innsung khalah siseh, thusimnak caan ka neih tikah nan hrangih bawmtu a si ding hmuahhmuah in zianghman suup loin ka sim ti khal nan thei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Judah mi hnenah siseh, Zentail mi hnenah siseh, an sualnak tlansan in Pathian hnenah an kir ih kan Bawi Jesuh an zum a ṭul hrimhrim tiah ka sim tlunah feltein ralrinnak khal ka pek hai a si.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule atu-ah Thlarau Thianghlim ih hruainak thlunin Jerusalem ah feh ka tum; cutawkah ziang ka cang ding ti zianghman ka thei lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Khawkip ah thawngtlak le harsatnak lawnglawng in in hngak a si ti lawng kha Thlarau Thianghlim ih ralrin peknak thawngin ka thei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sikhalsehla ka hrangah ka nunnak hi zianghman ah ka siar lo; Bawipa Jesuh in ṭuan dingih i pekmi Pathian ih zaangfahnak Thuthang ṭha phuan ding ṭuanvo hi famkim zetih ṭuan thluh thei ding lawng hi ka saduhthah a si.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nan zate hnenah a suk a so ah ka vak ih, Pathian ih Uknak thu ka lo sim. Asinain atu cu zohman in in hmu sal nawn lo ding, tihi ka thei.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Curuangah tuihsun ah hin fiangtein nan hnenah ka phuang: nanmah lakah pakhatkhat nan hloral asile kei in mawhthluk hlah uh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile Pathian ih tumtahmi kha suupmi zianghman nei loin a zatein nan hnenah ka phuang ṭheh a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cuti a si ruangah nanmah le nanmah kilkhawi awk thiam uhla Thlarau Thianghlim in tuurual kilkhawitu dingih a lo ret vekin nan tuurual kha ṭhatein kilkhawi uh. Pathian in a Fapa thisen thawn Amaió ta ih a tuah zomi a kawhhran khaaltu va si uh!",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kei ka feh hnuah ṭihnungza cinghnia hraang an ra ding ih tuuruun pawl hi an zoh meen lo ding, ti ka thei.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nanmah ih sung ihsi hin mihrek cun anmah lamih hruai duh ah thuphanper tahratin zumtu pawl hi an hruaisualnak tikcu caan a ra thleng ding.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Curuangah ralring uhla sun tilo zan tilo in mitthli thawn kum thum sung nan zatein ka lo zirhmi kha hngilh hlah uh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Atu cu Pathian kilkhawinak le a zaangfahnak thu sungah ka lo ap zo. Amah in a lo ṭhansoter ding ih a minung pawl hrangih a ret ciami thlawsuahnak kha a lo pek ding.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Zo ih tangka, sui le hnipuan khal ka daw dah lo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ka kut rori hin hna ka ṭuan ih keimah le ka rualpi pawl ih kan ṭulmi thil tla kha ka suahpi ve ti cu nan thei ṭhehmi a si ko.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ziang hmuahhmuah ah napi in ṭuan tahratin santlai lomi pawl kan bawm ding a si ti kha ka lo hmuh zo; Bawipa Jesuh khal in, ‘Ngah lam hnakin pek lamah lungawinak a tam sawn,’ a timi ṭongkam kha ciing ringring uh,” tiah thu a cah.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Paul in cutiin a sim ṭheh tikah a khuk a bil ih an zatein thla an cam tlang.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Paul cu an pom an hnam ih damte in vung feh aw, ti phahin an zatein an ṭap ciamco.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Zohman in in hmu sal nawn lo ding, a ti ruangah an riah a siat cuangnak a si. Cule lawng umnak tiang an hei thlah."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kannih khal in cibai kan buk ih kan feh. Long in khui hmanah taang phah loin kan feh ih Kos kan thleng; a thaisun ah Rhodes tikulh kan thleng ih cutawk ihsin Patara ah kan lanta.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutawkah Fonisia ih a feh dingmi lawng kan tong ih cuih lawng ah kan ceer ih kan feh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Saipras tikulh a lang theinak hmun kan thleng ih cutawk ihsin thlanglam ah kan her ih Siria lamah kan lan. Tai-ar khua ah kan ṭum ih cutawkah lawng thil phurhmi pawl an suahta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutawkah dungthluntu ṭhenkhat an um ih an hnenah zarh khat kan um. Thlarau ih simnak thawngin Paul cu Jerusalem ih feh lo dingin an dawn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sikhalsehla anmah thawn kan umtlang tikcu a cem tikah kan suak ih kan feh. Annih khal in an zatein an nupi le an faate pawl thawn tipikap tiang in thlah. Cutawkah kan zatein khukbil in thla kan cam tlang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule pakhat le pakhat cibai kan buk aw ih kannih lawng parah kan kai ih annih inn ah an tlung.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Tai-ar khua ihsin lawng in kan feh vivo ih Ptolemais kan thleng. Cutawkah zumtu unau pawl kan tong phah ih an hnenah ni khat kan caam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> A thaisun kan pok lala ih Sisaria kan thleng. Cutawkah Jerusalem ih upa pasarih hrilmi lakih pakhat a si mi Pathian thusimtu Filip ih inn ah kan riak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Pasal nei hrih lo fanu fala pali a nei ih Pathian thu a phuangtu profet an si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ni tam nawn kan um hnuah Judea ram ihsin profet pakhat Agabas an timi a ra thleng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kan hnenah a ra ih Paul ih taikhap a lak hnuah a kut le a ke kha cuih taikhap cun a ṭeem aw ih, “Thlarau Thianghlim in hiti in a ti: hi taikhap a neitu pa hi Jerusalem khua ah Judah mi pawl in hi bangtuk in an ṭeem ding ih Zentail mi pawl ih kut sungah an pe ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cumi kan theih tikah kanmah in siseh, midang khal in siseh, Paul cu Jerusalem ih feh lo dingin kan dawn ciamco.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sikhalsehla anih cun, “Ziangah so hiti ih nan um! Hiti nan ṭah ruangah ka lung in hnoter sinsin a si! Bawipa Jesuh hrangah cun Jerusalem khua sungah ṭeem le ṭawn lawng hman si loin thih ding tiang hman ka tiar a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ziangti hmanih kan don thei lo ruangah, “Bawipa ih duhnak vekin si ko seh,” tiah kan ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutawkah tikcu tawkfang sung kan um hnuah kan tim kan tuah ih Jerusalem ah kan feh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sisaria ih a ummi dungthlun ṭhenkhat pawl cun in thlun ve ih kan riahnak ding Mnason ih inn ah in fehpi. Mnason cu Saipras mi a si ih a hlan ihsin dungthluntu a rak si ringring.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Jerusalem kan vung thlen tikah zumtu unau pawl cun lungawi zetin in rak hmuak.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A thaisun ah Jeim tong dingin Paul thawn kan feh ih kawhhran upa pawl tla an kim ṭheh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Paul in cibai a buk hai hnuah an parih a lungawinak thu a sim ih a hnaṭuannak hmangin Pathian in Zentail mi lakih a tuahmi hmuahhmuah kha famkim zetin a sim.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cumi an theih tikah an zatein Pathian kha an thangṭhat. Cule annih in, “Kan u pa Paul, Judah mi pawl sungin mi thawng ziangzatso zumtu an cang zo ih Daan an thlunnak ah ziangtlukin taimak an suah ti cu na hmuh ṭhehmi a si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Zentail ram sungih a ummi Judah mi hmuahhmuah hnenah Moses Daan dungtun dingin le an faate pawl serhtan nawn lo dingin le Judah daan pawl thlun nawn lo dingin Paul in a zirh a si, tiah hitawk ummi pawl hin thu an thei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Atu-ah hitawk ih nan thlen zo hi an thei ding a si ih ziangtinso kan tuah ding?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hitiin tuah cila a ṭha ding tiah kan ruat. hittawk ah hin thukamnak a tuah zotu mi pali an um.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Anmah thawn va feh awla thianfainak ih tuah ṭheumi daan vekin va tuahpi ve awla an cemmi tangka tla va pek sak hai aw; cule an lu an meet thei ding. Cuti cun nangmah rori in Moses Daan kha na thlun ih na thuhla an rak theih ciami pawl hi thudik zianghman a um lo, ti kha an thei ṭheh ding.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Zentail mi pawl zumtu ih a cangmi pawl thuhla ahcun kanmah in ca kan kuat zo. Kan cakuatmi sungah cun milem hnenih pekmi tirawl ei lo ding, sathi ei lo ding, hngawngrek-ih thahmi sa ei lo ding, le nupa sualnak tuah lo ding, tiah kan relcatmi kha kan kuat zo a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cuhrangah Paul in a thaisun ah cuih mi pali cu a fehpi ih anmah thawn an daan vekin thianfainak cu an tuah. Cuih hnuah Biakinn sungah an lut ih thianfainak caan hi ziangtik ni ah a cem ding tile ziangtikah thawinak an pek fingfing a ṭulnak ding thu tla kha a sim.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ni sarih ni a kim zik tikah Asia ram ihsin a rami Judah mi ṭhenkhat pawl in Biakinn sungah Paul kha an hmu. Mipi pawl kha an tokhrok ih Paul cu an kai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Israel mi pawl, in bawm uh! Hi pa hi hmunzakipah feh tahratin Israel mi pawl siseh, Moses Daan siseh, hi Biakinn siseh, relsia in thu a zirh vivotu a si. Atu-ah hi Biakinn sungah hin Zentail mi pawl hman a ratpi ih hi hmun thianghlim hmuah a borhhlawhter thluh zo!” tiah an au.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> (Hitiih an aunak cu Efesa khuami Trofimas kha Paul thawn Jerusalem khawsungah an hmuh ruangah Biakinn sungah a luhpi a si, tiin an ruah ruangah a si.)",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Khawpi sung cu a zatein buainak in a khat ih misenpi cu an tlan ih Paul cu kai tahratin Biakinn sung ihsin an dirh suak. Cule hmakhatte-ah Biakinn sangka pawl cu an khar.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Misenpi in Paul cu thah an tum rero laiah Jerusalem khawpi an khawpum in ral an tho a si tiah Rom ralkap hotu ralbawipa hnenah thu an than.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hmakhatte-ah cuih ralbawipa cu ralbawi dang le ralkap pawl thawn an va tlan. Mipi in ralkap pawl thawn cuih ralbawipa an hmuh tikah Paul an vuak kha an baang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ralbawipa cu Paul hnenah a va feh ih a kaih hnuah thir cikcin pahnih in khit dingah thu a pek. Cule mipi cu, “Hi pa hi zoso a si? Ziang sualnak so a tuah?” tiah a sut.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Mipi sungih mi ṭhenkhat cu phunkhat in an au, mi hrekkhat cu phundang in an au ve. Thu a buaituk lawmmam ih, ralbawipa in ziang a cang ti a theih fiang lo ruangah a ralkap pawl kha Paul cu ṭankulh sungih luhpi dingin thu a pek.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> An fehpi tikah kailawn tiang lawng an thlenpi thei; cuih hnu cun misenpi pawl an neh thei lo ruangah Paul cu ralkap pawl in a zawn in an zawn.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> An dungin an rak nor vivo ih, “That uh,” tiah an au phah vivo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ralkap pawl in Paul cu ṭankulh sungih an luhpi zik zawng ah Paul in ralbawipa cu, “Thu pakhatte ka lo sim thei pei maw?” tiah a sut. Ralbawipa in, “Grik ṭong na thiam maw si?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cuti a si ahcun kan dung rei nawnah ral a tho ih hriamnam thawn mi thawngli ramṭhingih a tlanpitu Izipt pa kha cu na si lo ti aw?” tiah a sut.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Paul in, “Keimah cu Judah mi ka si. Silisia ram Tarsas khua ih a suakmi, khawpi hminthangih um ka si. Misenpi hnenah thusimnak tikcu i pe hram aw,” tiah a dil.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ralbawipa cun thusimnak tikcu a pek ih, curuangah Paul cu kailawn parah ding tahrat in mipi pawl cu dai dingin a zaa a zaap. Mipi pawl an daih tikah Paul in Hebru ṭong in an hnenah thu a sim."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Paul cun, “U le nau, nu le pa pawl, nan hmaiah hin ka ṭannak thu ka sim ve tikah hin i ngaihnik uh!” a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hebru ṭong ih a ṭong ruangah mipi cu an dai ṭhepṭhep. Cule Paul cun a hun peh sal ih:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Keimah cu Silisia peng Tarsas khua suak Judah mi ka si. Asinain Jerusalem khua ah a ṭhanglian mi ka si ih Gamaliel ih zirhmi ka si. Kan pupa pawl ih daan felzet le fekzet ih zirhmi ka rak si. Tuihsun hitawk ih a rami nanmah vekin Pathian hnenah pum petu ka rak si ve.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bawipa ih Lamzin thluntu pawl hi thi ko in ka rak hrem hai. Nunau tilo, mipa tilo in ka kai ih thawngah ka thlak.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Puithiam Saang le Khonsil upa pawl cu thudik ka simmi hi a theitu an si. Cuih upa pawl hnen ihsin Damaskas khua ih Judah unau pawl hnen pek ding ca ka keng ih Bawipa ih Lamzin thluntu pawl hi kai tahratih thir cikcin thawn khit in Jerusalem khua ih rak hruai dingin le hrem dingin Damaskas khua ah ka rak feh a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Cutiin ka feh ih Damaskas ka thlen zikah, sunlai hrawngah van ihsin a tleuzetmi tleunak in ka kimvel kha hmakhatte ah i run tlet.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Leilung ah ka tlu ih aw pakhat in, ‘Saul, Saul, ziangah so i hrem?’ tiah i ti kha ka thei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ‘Bawipa, zoso na si?’ tiah ka hun sut. Anih in, ‘Na hremmi Nazareth mi Jesuh ka si,’ tiah i ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka hawipi pawl in tleunak cu an hmu naón i biatu-ih aw cu an thei lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ‘Ziang so ka tuah ding, Bawipa?’ tiah ka sut. Bawipa in, ‘Tho awla Damaskas khawsungah va feh awla na tuah dingah Bawipa in a tumtah ciami hmuahhmuah kha an lo sim ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> A tleu tuk ruangah ka mit a caw ih ka rualpi pawl in ka kutin Damaskas khawsungah in hruai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuih khawpi ah Ananias cu daan thluntu saakhua-mi le cutawk ih um Judah mi hmuahhmuah ih upatmi a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ananias cu ka hnenah a ra ih ka kiangah ding tahratin, ‘Unau pa Saul, khua hmu sal aw,’ tiah a ti. Cuvete in khua ka hmu sal ih amah cu ka hun zoh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Amah in, ‘Kan pu le kan pa pawl ih Pathian in amah ih duhnak a theitu dingah le Miding pa hmutu dingah le amah ih aw rori a theitu dingah a lo hril zo a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ziangahtile na hmuhmi le na theihmi hi mi hmuahhmuah hnenih simtu dingah Amah ih thutheitu na si ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cuti a si ruangah reipi hngak nawn hlah! Tho awla amah ih hmin ko phah in baptisma lak awla na sualnak thiangfaiter aw,” tiah i ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Cuih hnuah Jerusalem ah ka kirsal ih Biakinn sungih thla ka cam laiah langnak ka hmu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih langnak ahcun Bawipa ka hmu ih ka hnenah, ‘Tho awla zamrangte in Jerusalem ihsin suak aw, ziangahtile hi khuami pawl in ka thuhla na phuanmi hi an pom lo ding,’ tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kei in, ‘Bawipa, sinakok ah ka feh ih nangmah a lo zumtu pawl kha kai in ka vuak rero ṭheu kha an theih ṭhehmi a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cule na thutheitu Stefen an thah tikah keimah rori ka um ih an thah kha ka lungkimpi tlunah a thattu pawl ih puan pawl a rak kensaktu ka si,’ tiah ka ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bawipa cun, ‘Feh ko aw; lam hlapi Zentail mi pawl hnenah ka lo thlah ding,’ i ti,” tiah Paul in a sim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cumi a sim tiang cu mipi pawl in ṭhatein an ngai. Asinain cuih hnu cun an aw neih patawp in, “Kha pa kha hloral seh! That uh! Nung ding a tlak lo!” tiah an au ciamco.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> An zatein an au, an kio, an hnipuan an zaap ih leivut kha vanah an khirh ciamco.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Rom ralbawipa in a ralkap pawl kha Paul hi ṭankulh sungah fehpi uhla ziang ruangah mipi pawl in hitlukin an hua ih an au hnawh ti theihnak dingah fung in vuak uh, tiah thu a pek.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sikhalsehla fung in vuak dingih an ṭem ṭheh tikah Paul in cutawkih a dingmi bawi pakhat hnenah, “A sual thu ṭhen hrih lo Rom mi pakhat hi vuak daan a si pei maw?” tiah a sut.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cuih thu a theih tikah cuih bawi cu ralbawipa hnenah a feh ih, “Ziang so na tuah? Khi pa khi Rom ih minung sokhaw a si!” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Curuangah Paul hnenah a va feh ih, “Rom mi na si maw? I sim hnik?” tiah ralbawipa cun a sut. “Ka si,” tiah Paul in a ti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ralbawipa in, “Kei khal tangka tampi ka pek hnuah ka si ve,” tiah a ti. Paul cun, “Kei cu ka suahkeh ihsin Rom mi ka si,” tiah a sawn.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cuvete in Paul thusuh a tumtu pawl cu dungah an siip ṭheh. Ralbawipa khal cu Paul kha Rom mi a si ti a theih tlunah Rom mi thir cikcin thawn a khih kha a theih sal tikah a thin a phangzet.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ralbawipa cun Judah mi pawl in Paul parih sual an puhmi hi ziang bik so a si, ti theihfiang a duh ruangah a thaisun ah Paul ih thir cikcin cu a phoihter ih Puithiam upa pawl le Khonsil upa an zatein tongkhawm aw dingah thu a pek. Cule Paul cu a hruai ih an hmaiah a dinter."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Paul in Khonsil upa pawl cu hmaiton tein a zoh hai ih, “Ka phunpi Israel mi pawl, tuihsun tiang Pathian hmaiih ka nunzia ahhin phuhrun awknak malte hman ka nei lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Puithiam Saang Ananias in Paul kiangih a dingmi pawl hnenah Paul kha a kaa ah hei beng dingin thu a pek.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah Paul in, “Nang siirang hnihmi phar, Pathian in nangmah a lo beng ding a si. Daan vekih ka thu rel dingah kha tawkah na to; asinain ‘Hei beeng uh,’ tiih thu na peknak in cuih Daan cu na buar a si!” tiah a sawn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Paul kiangih a ummi pawl in, “Pathian ih Puithiam Saang na hmuhsuam a si!” tiah Paul cu an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Paul cun, “Israel mi u le nau pawl, Puithiam Saang a si ti ka thei lo! Ca Thianghlim sungah, ‘Na miphun a uktu na relsiat lo pei,’ tiin a um a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Paul in a rami pawl lakah a hrek cu Sadusi an si ih a hrek cu Farasi an si, ti kha a hmuh tikah Khonsil upa hmaiah cun a au ih, “Ka phunpi Israel mi pawl, kei hi Farasi ka si, Farasi pawl ih fapa ka si. A thimi pawl an nung sal ding, tiih ruahsannak ka neih ruangah atu hitawk ah hin tazacuainak ka tong,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutiih a sim ṭheh vete in Farasi le Sadusi pawl cu an to aw ih cutawkih a ummi pawl lakah ṭhenṭhek awknak a suak.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> (Ziangahtile Sadusi pawl cun minung hi an thih hnuah cun an thosal nawn lo ding; vancungmi khal an um lo, thlarau khal an um lo, tiah an ti. Asinain Farasi pawl cun a pathum tein a um tiah an zum.)",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An au cu a ring deuhdeuh ih Farasi a si mi Daanthiam hrekkhat pawl an ding ih nasa zetin an au ve: “Hi pa sualnak hi malte hman kan hmu lo. Thlarau a si lole vancungmi in a hnenah a sim ngaingai a si thei meen sokhaw!” tiah an ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nasa tukih an tawh awk ruangah Paul kha an bauhthlek thluh ding tiah ralbawipa a thin a phang. Curuangah mipi lak ihsin Paul kha vung hruai ih ṭankulh ih fehpi dingin a ralkap pawl thu a pek.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cuih zanah cun Bawipa cu Paul kiangah a ding ih, “Paul, zianghman ṭih hlah! Hitawk Jerusalem khua ah ka thu theihpitu na si zo, hivek thotho in Rom khua khalah na si hrih ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A thaizing ah Judah mi ṭhenkhat pawl an tongkhawm aw ih khua an khang. Paul an thah thei hlanah cun rawl ei lo ding le tidai khal in lo dingin thu an kam aw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hitiin hmun khatih khua a khangtu hi minung sawmli leng lo an si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutiin Puithiam upa le upa dang pawl hnenah an feh ih, “Paul kan thah thei hlanah cun zianghman ei lo le in lo dingin thu kan kam aw zo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah nanmah le Khonsil pawl in Rom ralbawipa hnenah thu hei cah uhla, Paul thuhla kim deuh in theih kan duh, tiin ti awter uhla, Paul kha hitawk ah run hruaiter uh. Cule kannih in kan rak bawh pei ih hitawk a thlen man hlanah kan rak that pei,” tiah an ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul farnu-ih fapa in cutiih an phiarthupmi cu a theih ruangah ṭankulh-ah cun a feh ih Paul kha a va sim.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule Paul in ralbawi pakhat kha a ko ih a hnenah, “Hi tlangvalpa hi ralbawipa hnenah hei hruai aw; thuruah ding pakhat a nei,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cuih ralbawi cun a hruai ih an hotu ralbawipa hnenah a fehpi ih, “Thawngtla pa Paul in i ko ih hi tlangvalpa hi na hnenih ratpi dingah i fial, ziangahtile thu pakhat lo sim ding a nei,” tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> An hotu ralbawipa cun tlangvalpa cu a kut in a hruai ih anmah pahnih lawng an feh ih, “Ziang so i ruah duh?” tiah a sut.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Tlangvalpa cun, “Judah mi hotu upa pawl in Paul thuhla-ah Khonsil pawl in famkim deuh in thu theih an duh tiah an ti-awter ding ih thaisun ah Paul kha Khonsil upa hnenah run hruai dingin lo dil dingah lungkimnak an nei zo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sikhalsehla an thu cu ngai hlah aw; ziangahtile minung sawmli leng lo in Paul kha an rak bawh ding. Paul an thah hlanah cun zianghman ei lo le in lo dingin thu an kam aw. Atu-ah an ralring aw thluh zo ih nangmah ih thurelcat dingmi lawng an hngak lai,” tiah a sim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ralbawipa cun, “Ka hnenih na simmi hi zo ih hnen hmanah va phuang hlah,” tiah a ti ih tlangvalpa cu a tlunter.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cule ralkap hotu ralbawipa cun a kuthnuai ralbawi pahnih a ko ih, “Sisaria ih feh dingah ralkap zahnih timtuah uh. Cule rang ralkap sawmsarih le feipi ralkap zahnih khal timtuah uhla tuihzan nazi pakua ih suak thei dingin ralring hai seh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Paul ih to dingah rang tla ngaihtuah uhla Mangki bawi Felix hnenah himte in thlenter uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule ralbawipa in a tanglam vekin ca a kuat.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Klaudius Lisias in Mangki Bawipa Felix hnenah cibai bukin ca ka lo kuat.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na hnenih ka hun kuat mipa hi Judah mi pawl in an kai ih a thah an tum. Rom mi a si ti ka thei ih ka ralkap pawl thawn kan va run suak.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> A sual an puhmi hi ziang a si bik ti theih duh ah Khonsil upa hnenah ka fehpi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ka theih ngah tikah a tuahmi cu thah tlak sualnak a si lo ih thawng thlak tlak sualnak khal a si lo; sual an puhmi cu anmah ih daan thuhla men khi a si.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cule amah thah duh ah khua an khang ti ka theih ruangah hmakhatte ah na hnenah ka hun kuat. Sual a puhtu pawl khal cu na hnenah ra in na hmai rori ih tazacuai dingin ka sim hai a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ralbawipa ih thupekmi vekin ralkap pawl cun an tuah. Paul cu an hruai ih cuih zanah Antipatris tiang an fehpi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> A thaizing ah lei ralkap pawl cu an kir ih rang ralkap pawl in an thlun.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Sisaria khua an thlenpi ih Mangki Bawipa kutah cakuat cu an pek hnuah a kut sungah Paul cu an ap.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Mangki Bawipa in cakuat cu a siar ih, “Khuitawk pengin so na rat?” tiah Paul kha a sut. Silisia pengin a si, ti a theih tikah a hnenah,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Thu a lo khingtu pawl an thlen tikah na thu cu ka rel leh ding,” tiah a ti. Cule Paul cu Siangpahrang Herod ih a rak sakmi innpi Mangki Bawipa ih zung sungah ralkap ih kil dingin thu a pek."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ni nga hnuah Puithiam Saang Ananias cu upa ṭhenkhat le sih-ni Tertullas thawn Sisaria ah an feh. Mangki Bawipa Felix hmaiah an suak ih Paul taza an cuainak cu an sim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule Paul cu an ko ih sih-ni Tertullas cun Paul sual an puhnak thu cu hiti in a sim: “Mangki Bawipa, fimnak thawn nangmah in in hruai ruangah caan reipi daihnak kan ngah ih kan ram ṭhatnak hrangah rem ṭulmi pawl tampi rem a si zo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Himi kan hmuh tikah na tuahmi pawl hi khuazakipah mi in an pom ih na parah kan lung a awi ngaingai.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na tikcu tamtuk ka lo laksak pang ding ti ka phan ruangah kan sim duhmi kha a tawi thei sungin kan hun sim pei ih zaangfahte in in ngaisak hram aw.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Himi pa hi mi buaiter theizet le ṭihnungza a si tiin kan hmu. Leilung tlun hmun kipih Judah mi pawl a buaiter ringring ih Nazareth bu an timi pawl sungah hruaitu amah hi a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kan Biakinn borhhlawhter a tum ih culai ah kan kai. (Cule kan daan vekin a thu rel kan tum;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> asinain ralbawipa Lisias a ra ih hranhram in in ra long.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cuih hnuah Lisias in Paul tazacuai a duhtu pawl cu na hnenah hin feh hai seh, tiah thu a pek.) Nangmah in hi pa hi thu na sut ahcun amah ih hnen ihsin sual kan puhmi pawl hi nangmah rori in na thei ko ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutiih a simmi cu Judah mi pawl in an bawm ih a simmi hi a zatein a dik ṭheh a si an ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Mangki Bawipa in Paul cu thu sim dingah a kut in a zaap ih Paul in Mangki Bawipa hnen ah: “Nangmah cu hi ram sungah hin kum reipi thureltu a ṭuantu na si ti ka thei ih atu-ah na hmaiah ka ṭanhmun sim dingin caan ka neih ruangah ka lung a awizet.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Jerusalem ah Pathian bia dingin ka hung fehnak hi ni hleihnih hnakin a tam hrih lo, ti cu na thei ko ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Biakinn sungah zo thawn hman thu kan el aw lo, ti cu Judah mi in an thei ṭheh. Sinakok ah siseh, khawpi sung hmun dangdang khalah siseh, misenpi ka tokhroknak an hmu hrimhrim lo ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule atu-ah na hmaiih sual in puhmi pawl hi a dik taktak a si tiah an lo hmuh thei fawn lo ding.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ka tuah taktak tiin na hmaiah ka ti duhmi cu hihi a si: Kan pupa pawl ih Pathian ka biaknak ah hin Lamzin kan timi ka thlun; annih in cuih Lamzin cu a dik lo an ti. Sikhalsehla Moses Daan sungih nganmi hmuahhmuah le profet pawl ih nganmi cabu sung ummi hmuahhmuah khal ka zummi an si ṭheh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Anmah vek thothoin keimah khal Pathian hnenah ruahsannak ka nei ve. Cuih ruahsannak cu, mi hmuahhmuah in, miṭha khal misia khal, thihnak ihsin an tho sal ding, timi a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cuti cun Pathian hmai le minung hmaiah phuhrun awknak nei lo dingin ka zuam thei tawk ka zuam ringring.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Kum reipi sung Jerusalem khua ka thlen nawn lo ruangah ka miphun pawl bomnak ah tangka pe ding le thawinak pe dingin Jerusalem ah ka hung feh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A daan vekin thianfainak ka tuah ṭheh hnuah a tlunih ka simmi pawl ka tuah rero laiah Biakinn sungah in hmu. Culai ah ka hnenah miburpi an um lo; buainak khal a um lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Asinain cutawkah cun Asia ram ihsin a rami Judah mi hrekkhat an um. Cupawl cu ka parah lungkimlonak an neih a si ahcun na hmai rori-ah hin anmah ra in mawhthluknak cu ra sim ve ding an si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Asilole hitawk ih a um pawl hin Khonsil upa pawl hmaiih ka din laiah ka sual tiih an hmuhmi lo sim hai seh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> An hmaiih ka din laiah thil pakhat lawng ka aupi mi a um: ‘Mithi pawl cu nunnak ah an tho sal ding,’ tiin ka zum ruangah tuihsun ah hin thu in khiing a si,” tiah a sim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule Felix cu cuih Lamzin thuhla ṭha zetih a theitu a si ruangah an thu rel cu a cawlter ih, “Ralbawipa Lisias a ra thlen tikah nan thu cu ka rel leh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Paul a kiltu ralbawi cu, “Paul hi ṭhatein kilveng uhla, malte in luatter deuh uhla a ṭul a haimi pawl cu a rualpi pawl in pe hai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ni malte a rei hnuah Felix cu a nupi Drusilla thawn an ra. Drusilla cu Judah mi a si. Paul kha a ko ih Paul in Jesuh Khrih zumnak thuhla kha a sim ih cumi cu an ngai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul in ṭhatnak thu, mah le mah suup awknak thu le a ra thleng dingmi Thuṭhennak Ni thu pawl a sim tikah Felix cu a thin a phang ih, “Tu cu va kir hrih aw. Tikcu ka neih tikah ka lo ko sal leh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Felix cun Paul in tangka i pe sehla tiah ruahsannak a nei. Curuangah Paul cu a ko leuhleuh ih thu a ruahpi ṭheu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kum hnih a rei hnuah Mangki Felix cu Porsius Festas in a hnaṭuan a thleng. Judah mi pawl hnen ihsin mithmai ṭha ngah a duh ruangah Felix in Paul cu suah loin thawng sungah a taanta."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Festas cu cuih ram a thlennak ni thum hnuah Sisaria ihsin Jerusalem ah a feh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutawkah Puithiam upa pawl le Judah mi hotu pawl in Paul parih sual an puhnak thuhla pawl cu an rak sim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Paul cu lamzin ih thah an duh ruangah Jerusalem ah run hruai dingin Festas cu an dil.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Festas in, “Paul cu Sisaria khua ih thawngtlami a si ih keimah khal Sisaria ah ka kir cing ding.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Nan hotu pawl cu keimah thawn Sisaria ah ra hai sehla himi pa in sualnak a neih a si ahcun ra sim hai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Festas cu an hnenah ni riat a si lole ni hra hrawng a caam hnuah Sisaria ah a tlung. Inn a thlen ih thaisun ah Festas cu a thurelnak zung sungah a to ih Paul cu rak hruai dingin thu a pek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Paul cu a ra thleng ih Jerusalem ihsin a rami Judah mi pawl cu a kiangkap ah an ding vialvial ih nasa zetin sual an puh; asinain sual an puhmi cu a dik taktakmi a si tiah an langter thei lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul cu a ṭang ve ih, “Judah mi daan thu-ah siseh, Biakinn thu-ah siseh, Rom siangpahrang ih thu-ah siseh, sualnak zianghman ka tuah lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Asinain Judah mi hnen ihsin mithmai ṭha ngah a duh ruangah Festas in Paul cu, “Jerusalem ah feh in cutawkah ka hmaiah taza lo cuai hai sehla na lung a kim pei maw?” tiah a sut.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Paul in, “Rom Siangpahrang ih thurelnak hmaiah atu hi ka ding ih hitawk ah taza in cuai hai seh. Nangmah ih na theih vekin Judah mi hnenah thilsual zianghman ka tuah lo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Daan ka buar ih thihnak tlak thilsual ka tuahmi a um ahcun luat ningla tiah ka dil lo. Sikhalsehla sual in puhmi ah hin thudik zianghman a um lo a si ahcun zohman in Judah mi pawl kut sungah in thlenpi thei lo ding. Rom Siangpahrang hnenah azu ka khan a si!” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule Festas in amah ruahnak petu pawl thawn an tonkhawm awk hnuah Paul cu, “Rom siangpahrang hnenih azu na khan vekin a hnenah na feh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuih hnu caan tawkfang a rei hnuah Siangpahrang Agrippa le Bernis cu Festas cibai buk ih biata dingin Sisaria ah an ra tlawng.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ni rei nawn an caam hnuah Festas in Paul ih thuhla cu siangpahrang Agrippa hnenah cun a sim. “Felix in thawngih a thlakta mipa pakhat Sisaria ah hin a um.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Jerusalem ih khual ka vung tlawn laiah Judah mi puithiam upa pawl le upa dang pawl in taza an cuai ih amah cu thah dingah in dil.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asinain ka sim mi cu: Kannih Rom mi pawl cun mi pakhatkhat taza an cuai tikah tazacuaitu thawn hmaiton tein amah a ṭannak thu simnak caan a neih ve hlanah cun tazacuai mipa kha an kut sungih pek cu kan daan a si lo, tiah ka ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hitawkih an rat tikah ni khat hman hngak loin a thaisun rori-ah thurelnak zungah ka to ih cupa cu rak hruai uh tiah thu ka pek.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Amah a duh lotu pawl cu an ding ih thu an sim, asinain sual an puh hmang ding tiih ka ruah tlukin an puh lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> An biaknak thu le Jesuh an timi pa a thi ih Paul in, ‘A nungsal,’ tiih a simmi ruangah thu el awknak an rak nei a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hi thuhla-ah hin ziangtinso thufiang ka theih thei ding, tiah ka thinlung ka ṭhen aw thei lo; curuangah Paul cu Jerusalem ah feh in sual an lo puhmi thu hi cutawkah rel sehla na lung a kim pei maw?” tiah ka sut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul cun azu a khan ih amah khal kil hrih ding le Rom Siangpahrang ih a thu rel leh ding in a dil. Curuangah amah kha Rom siangpahrang hnenih ka kuat thei hlan cu ralkap pawl ih kil dingah thu ka pek a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Agrippa in Festas cu, “Cupa ih thusimmi cu keimah rori in theih ve ka duh,” tiah a ti. Festas in, “Thaisun ah na thei ding,” a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A thaisun ah Agrippa le Bernis cu sunglawi zet le ropi zetin, tonkhawmnak khaan sungah cun an vung lut ih ralbawi upa bik pawl le khawsung tlangsuak upa pawl in an thlun. Cule Festas ih thupeknak vekin Paul cu an vun hruai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Festas in, “Siangpahrang Agrippa le hitawk ih a rami pawl: Hi nan hmuh mipa hi Judah mi hmuahhmuah in, hitawk ah siseh Jerusalem ah siseh, an duh lonak thu ka hnenih an thlentermi a si. Nung tlak a si lo ti tiangin an au.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sikhalsehla thah tlak sualnak a tuahmi ka hmu thei lo. Cule amah in Rom siangpahrang hnenih azu a khan ruangah cutawkih kuat dingin thu ka relcat zo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asinain Rom siangpahrang hnenih a thuhla ngan ding felfai-in ka thei tuk lo. Curuangah atu-ah nan hmaiah hin ka rak hruaiter. Siangpahrang Agrippa, nangmah ih hmai rori-ah ka hun suahpi. A thuhla ka zingzoi hnuah ngan ding ziangtal ka nei pei maw, ti duh ah a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile keimah ih hrang hrimhrim ah thawngtla pakhat thu an khiinnak thuhla zianghman fiangtein ngan loih kuat cu a mawi lo a si,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Agrippa in Paul hnenah, “Na thuhla cu na sim thei,” tiah a ti. Paul in a kut a hun thlir ih a ṭannak thu cu hiti in a sim:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Siangpahrang Agrippa, tuihsun nangmah ih hmaiah Judah mi pawl ih sual in puhmi thu pawl let ve theinak caan ka ngah ruangah mi vanṭha ngaingai ka si tiah ka ruat aw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Judah mi daan hmuahhmuah le thu an el awknak pawl a thei ṭhehtu na si ruangah mi vanṭha ih ka ruah awk cuangnak cu a si. Thinsautein i ngai hram aw, tiah zaangfah ka lo dil.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Judah mi pawl hmuahhmuah in ka nuncan daan cu ka nauhak lai ihsin in thei ṭheh. Ka nuncan khuasaknak thuhla pawl, a hmaisa-ah keimah ih miphun hnenah, a neta-ah Jerusalem ah, a zatein an theih ṭhehmi a si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka thuhla cu sim an duh a si ahcun an sim pei, an theih ringring mi a si. A hramthok ihsin kei cu kan biaknak lamah cun a fektukmi Farasi pawl ih sungtel ka si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tuihsun hitawk ah ka thu rel dingin ka dinnak khal hi Pathian in kan pu le kan pa pawl hnenih thukamnak a tuahmi kha ruahsannak ka neih ruangah a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutiih ruahsannak ka neihmi cu kan miphun phun hleihnih pawl in Pathian kha a sun a zan in an rak biak laiih ruahsannak an rak neih mi thotho a si. Cuih ruahsannak ruangah cun Siangpahrang Bawipa, Judah mi pawl in taza in cuainak hi a si!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hitawkih a rami pawl, Pathian in mithi a thawhter tihi ziangah so a cang thei lomi thilah nan ruat?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Nazareth mi Jesuh ih thuhla cu ka do thei tawkin ka do ding, tiah keimah rori in ka rak ruah dahmi a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cumi cu Jerusalem khua ih ka rak tuah rero dahmi a si. Puithiam upa pawl hnen ihsin thuneihnak ka ngah ih Pathian minung pawl tampi thawngah ka thlak. Thah dingih thurel an si tikah ka lungkimnak langternak ah ka kut ka rak tung ve ṭheu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Voi tampi sinakok sung rori-ah ka hremter hai ih an zumnak bansan hai seh tiah ka zuam thei tawkin ka rak zuam. An parah ka thin a heng tuk ih anmah hrem dingin ramdang khua pawl tiang ka thleng dah a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Cutiin anmah hrem duh rori-ah cun Puithiam upa pawl hnen ihsin thuneihnak ca ka lak ih Damaskas khua ah ka feh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Maw siangpahrang Bawipa, sun laifangih Damaskas lamzinih ka feh rero laiah ni hnakin a tleu deuhmi tleunak van ihsin a rung thleng ih keimah le ka fehpi mi pawl ih kimvel kha a run tlet.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kan zatein leilungah kan tlu ih Hebru ṭong in aw pakhat ka thei ih, ‘Saul, Saul, ziangah so i hrem rero? Cawcang in a neitu pa ih fung a saih tikah amah a natter awk sawn vekin nangmah na nater aw sawn a si,’ tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ‘Bawipa, zoso na si?’ tiah ka sut. Cule Bawipa in, ‘Na hremmi Jesuh ka si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tho awla na ke in ding aw. Keimah i rian dingin ka lo hril duh ruangah na hnenah ka lang a si. Tuihsun ih kei i tonnak thu le hmailamih ka lo hmuh dingmi thu pawl hi midang hnenah na sim pei ih ka thutheitu na si pei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nangmah cu Israel mi le Zentail mi hnenah ka lo thlah ding ih an kutsung ihsin ka lo runsuak ding.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> An mit na mengter ding ih thimnak sung ihsin tleunak ah, Satan cahnak sung ihsin Pathian hnenah na kirter hai ding. Cuti cun keimah in zumnak thawngin an sualnak tla cu ngaidam an si ding ih Pathian ih thianhlimtermi pawl lakah an tel ve ding,’ tiah i ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Cuti a si ruangah, Siangpahrang Agrippa, van ihsin langnak ka hmuhmi ih thu cu ka el thei lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hmaisabik ah Damaskas khua ah, cule Jerusalem khua ah, cuih hnuah Judea ramsung hmuahhmuah le Zentail mi hnen khalah ka feh ih, ‘Nan sual siir aw uhla Pathian hnenah kir uh; cule nan sualsirnak langtertu hnaṭuan kha ṭuan uh,’ tiah thu ka sim vivo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutiih ka ti ruangah Judah mi pawl in Biakinn sungah in kai ih a thah tiangin in tum a si.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla tuihsun tiangah hin Pathian in i bawm ih atu-ah, nanmah a tum a seen ti loin nan zate hmaiah ka hmuhmi thu cu ka sim a si. Ka simmi thu hi Moses in siseh, profet pawl in siseh a cang ding tiih an rak sim ciami an si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cutiih an simmi cu ziang a si tile: tleunak rundamnak thu cu Judah mi le Zentail mi pawl hnenih than dingah Messiah in tuarnak a tong ding ih, cuih hnuah thihnak ihsin a nungsaaltu hmaisa bik a si ding, ti a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Paul in a ṭannak thuhla cutiin a sim tikah Festas in, “Paul, na aa zo a si! Na zir tamtuknak in a lo aatter zo a si hi!” tiah a hei auh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cutikah Paul in, “Bawipa Festas, ka aa lo sokhaw! Lungfim tein thutak ka lo sim a si!",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Maw Siangpahrang Agrippa, na hnenah cun suupmi nei lo ralṭha zetin ka ṭong; ziangahtile nang cu hi thu pawl hmuahhmuah hi a thei ṭhehtu na si. Pakhat hman hrelh loin na hminsin ṭheh ko ding tiah ka zum, ziangahtile hiti ih ka simmi pawl hi zo ih theih lomi, a kelkawm-ih thuhmi pawl an si lo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Siangpahrang Agrippa, profet pawl na zum maw? Na zum a si, ti ka thei!” tiah a ti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Agrippa in Paul cu, “Hi tikcu tawite sungah Khristian canter i tum maw si?” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Paul in, “A caan tawite ah siseh, caan saupi ah siseh, nangmah le tuihsun hitawk ih ka thu a ngaitu hmuahhmuah hi nan zatein, hi ka kutih thir cikcin siarlo, keimah vek si ṭheh uhla tihi Pathian hnenih ka thlacamnak a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cule Siangpahrang Bawipa, Mangki Bawipa, Bernis le midang pawl tla an tho ih,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> an feh hnuah pakhat le pakhat, “Hi pa hi thah tlak le thawng thlak tlak sualnak a tuahmi a um ual lo,” tiah an ti aw.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Cun Agrippa in Festas hnenah, “Rom siangpahrang hnenah azu khan hlah sehla, hi pa hi thlah theih mai a si ko ding naón!” tiah a ti."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Italy ah lawng ih feh dingin thu relcat a si tikah Paul le thawngtla dang pawl cu Rom ralkap “Siangpahrang Ralkap Burpi,” timi a hotu ralbawi Julius kutah an pek.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Asia ram tangphawlawng colhnak hmun pawl a pal phah vivo ding mi Adramittium khua ihsin a rami tangphawlawng to in kan feh. Masidonia ram Thesalonika khuami Aristarkas khal kan hnenah a tel ve.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A thaisun ah Sidon kan thleng. Julius cu Paul parah zaangfahnak thinlung a nei ih Paul cu a ṭulmi thilri pawl a ngah theinak dingah a rualpi pawl va leen le va ton theinak tikcu tla a pek.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutawk ihsin kan feh ih thli kanmah lam lawnglawngih a hran ruangah Saipras tikulh thli-upnak lam in kan feh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tifinriat kha Silisia le Pamfilia zawn ihsin kan tan ih Lisia ram Mira khua kan thleng.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cutawkah ralbawipa cun Alexandria ihsin Italy ih a feh dingmi tangphawlawng a hmu ih cuih tangphawlawng ahcun in fehter.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nuamtete in kan feh ih ni tampi kan rei hnuah a netnak ah harzet in Snidas khua zawn kan thleng. Cutawklam zawh in feh ding thli in in kham ruangah Krete tikulh leilung phen thli-upnak lam ihsin kan feh ih Salmon ram-forhlei kiang ihsin kan lan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tifinriat kap naih in kan feh vivo ih harzet in Himnak Longcolh Hmun an timi kan thleng. Cumi cu La sia khua ihsin a hlat lo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutawkah cun reipi kan cawl ih Sualtlennak Ni a luan zo ih tangphawlawng in khualtlawn cu ṭihnung a si thlang. Curuangah Paul in hiti in an hnenah ruahnak a pek:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “U le nau pawl, hi tawk ihsin kan lamzin cu ṭihnungza a si ding. Nan phurhmi thilri le tangphawlawng hi siatralnak a tong ding ih kan nunnak khal a cemral ding a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul ih simmi hnakin tangphawlawng neitupa ih simmi sawn kha ralbawipa ih thinlung sungah a lut.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cuih an tangphawlawng colhnak cu thlatang tikcu ahcun umnak a ṭhat lo ruangah mi tam sawn cun a cang thei a si ahcun Finiks thleng feh lawlaw ih cutawkih thlatang sung um kha an duh. Finiks cu Krete tikulh ih tangphawlawng colhnak a si ih thlanglam nitlaknak lam le saklam nitlaknak lam hoi in a um.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Thlanglam ihsin simthli neemte a hung hrang ih an tumtah vekih feh thei dingin an ruat. Curuangah tangphawlawng hrennak thirkawn kha ti sungin an hnuk ih Krete tikap naih vivo in kan feh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Asinain rei lote-ah, “Nisuah Saklam Zothlipi,” cak zetin Krete lam ihsin a rung hrang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kan tangphawlawng cu a run deen ih cuih thli cu kan pah thei nawn lo ruangah beidong in kan um ih kan tangphawlawng cu thli in a duhnak poh ah a fehpi vivo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kauda tikulh ih thlanglam kan thlen tikah cun thli in phen deuh ruangah a zia a um deuh. Cutawkah cun harsa zetin tangphawlawng ih a kenmi vokkuanglawng cu rem deuhin kan ret.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Tangphawlawng parah vokkuanglawng cu an vun hnuk ih hri in tangphawlawng ahcun fektein an ṭemcih. Libia ram tikap kiangih ti sungih vunnel tlangtluan pah ding an phan ruangah tangphawlawng cu a puanzar an ṭhum ih thli in a duhduhnak ah a so ih.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thlipi a hrang thotho ih a thaisun ahcun tangphawlawng ih phurhmi thilri hrekkhat cu ti sungah an hlon.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A tipsun ah tangphawlawng ih thilthuam hrekkhat an hlon.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ni tampi sung, ni le arsi pawl kan hmu thei lo; thli cu nasa zetin a hrang ringring. A netnak ahcun kan nung ding ti ruahsannak malte hman kan nei nawn lo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tangphawlawng parih mi pawl cu rawl loin ni tampi an um hnuah an hmaiah Paul a ding ih, “Unau pawl, ka thusimmi in ngai uhcila Krete tikulh ihsin feh loin um nungla hi bangtuk cemnak le ralnak hi kan tong lo ding.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla atu-ah nan thinphang hlah uh, tiah ka lo sim. Tangphawlawng hi cu kan sung ding naón kanmah cu kan hloral lo ding.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ziangahtile mizanah i neitu le ka biakmi Pathian ih vancungmi ka hnenah a rung ih,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ‘Paul, ṭih hlah aw! Rom siangpahrang ih hmaiah na din a ṭul a si! Pathian na parih a ṭhat ruangah nangmah thawn a fehmi pawl hi pakhat hman thi lotein an nunnak a zuah ṭheh ding,’ tiah i ti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Curuangah unau pawl, phang hlah uh! Ziangahtile Pathian ka rinsan ih i sim cia vek cekci in a si ko ding.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asinain tikulh pakhatkhatah thli in in soih ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Zan hleilinak a si zo, Mediterranean Tifinriat ahcun thlipi in in hrual ciamco. Zanṭim hrawngah tangphawlawng kiltu pawl in leilung kan naih thlang hmang tiah an zum deuh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Curuangah hri in thirtum an khih ih an vun thlak ih tidai cu pi zakhat le pi kul a thuuk. Malte hnuah an thlak sal ih pi sawmkua a si.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Tangphawlawng in lungpi a sawh pang ding ti an phan ruangah a dunglam ihsin a hrennak thirkawn pali an thlak ih thlacam phahin khuavan ding an hngak.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cule lawng hnaṭuan pawl cu tlan an tum; vokkuanglawng kha ti sungah an vun ṭhum ih a hmailam ihsin a hrennak thirkawn ṭhenkhat thla ding vekin an um awter.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Sikhalsehla ralbawipa le ralkap pawl hnenah cun Paul in, “Tangphawlawng kiltu pawl tangphawlawng parih an um lo asile nan nun ding ruahsannak zianghman a um lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Curuangah vokkuanglawng a kaitu hri pawl cu ralkap pawl in an satcat ih vokkuanglawng cu an fen hloter.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Khua a van deuh hlanah Paul in rawl ei dingin a fial hai: “Ni hleili sung lungphangin nan um zo ih hi sung hmuahhmuah ah zianghman nan ei lo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Zaangfah ka lo dil: rawl malte tal ei thlang uh. Nan nunnak dingah a ṭul a si. Nan lu parih samphang pakhat hman a hloral lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Cutiih a ti hnuah Paul in saang malte a lak ih an zate hmaiah Pathian hnenah thlacam in saang cu a phel ih a ei.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Midang khal an thinlung a hung cak deuh ih rawl malte an ei fingfing.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Tangphawlawng parih a ummi cu kan zatein zahnih le sawmsarih le paruk kan si.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Tawkfang an ei ṭheh hnuah sangvut hmuahhmuah kha tifinriat sungah an hlon ṭheh ih cuti cun tangphawlawng kha zaang deuh in an tuah.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Khua a vang tikah tangphawlawng kiltu pawl in tikap an hmuh tikah khui ram a si ti an thei thei lo. Asinain tikel ih tikap pakhat an hmu ih a cang thei asile cutawkih an tangphawlawng colhter kha an tum.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Curuangah an tangphawlawng hrennak hri cu an satcat ih a thirkawn cu tifinriat sungah an pilter; cule tangphawlawng hlaunak hri in an ṭemmi an phoih. Cun tangphawlawng hmailam bikah a puanzar kha an zaar ih thli in hmailam ah a sem ih tikap lamah cun kan feh.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Asinain tangphawlawng cun vunnel pawng a sawh ih a taang. A hmailam cu vunnel sungah a dawt aw ih a phuak aw thei nawn lo; a dunglam cu tisuar in a hrual ciamco ih a phel kuai thluh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ralkap pawl cun thawngtla pawl kha ti an leuh ding ih titlang an thlen tikah an tlanhlo thluh ding ti an phan ruangah thah ṭheh hai an tum.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Asinain ralbawipa in Paul kha a hum duh ruangah a kham hai. Cule ti a leuh thei pawl cu tangphawlawng ihsin dawp dingah le tikap ah leuh dingin thu a pek.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> A taangmi pawl in thingpheng maw, tangphawlawng a kuaimi thingphel maw, an pom ih an thlun. Cuti cun kan zatein tikap ah himte in kan thleng."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Himteih tikap kan thlen tikah cuih tikulh cu Malta tikulh a si ti kan thei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutawkih a rak ummi minung pawl cu kan parah an ṭhazet. Ruah a sur ih a daih tuk ruangah kan hrangah meipi in tih sak ih ṭhazet in in zoh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Paul in thinghreu a va khawm ih meipi-ah cun a thlak. Mei a sat ruangah thing sung ihsin rul a hung suak ih Paul ih kut kha a cuk ih a thlai aw niarniar.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Paul ih kut parih rul a thlai awk niarniar an hmuh tikah cutawk tikulh ih minung pawl cun, “Hi pa hi laithat a si ding, tifinriat sung ihsin a luat naón laireltu a khawzing in a nunter lo ding a si hi!” tiah an ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sikhalsehla Paul in rul cu meisa sungah a thinthlak ih amah cu a zianghman a poi lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ziangtikah so a hung thlin uun-o ding, a si lole ziangtikah so a sawn ruangro ding, ti kha cutawkih mi pawl cun an hngak. Asinain reizet an hngak ih ziangti hmanih a um lo kha an hmuh tikah an thinlung an thleng sal ih, “Amah hi pathian a si ding!” tiah an ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutawk ihsin a nai nawn ah loram a kau nawn a um ih a neitu cu cuih tikulh ih lalpa Publias a si. Publias cun ṭhazet in in zoh ih ni thum sung a mikhual ah kan cang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Publias ih pa cu khurhnat le thisen sungdok in a na ih ihkhun ah a it ringring. A ihnak khaan sungah Paul a lut ih a parah a kut suangin thla a cam ih a dam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cuih thu an theih tikah cuih tikulh ih midam lo hmuahhmuah an ra ih an dam ṭheh ve.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Laksawng tampi in pek ih tangphawlawng in kan feh tikah lamzin hrangih kan ṭul dingmi pawl tla tangphawlawng parah in ret sak.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Thla thum hnuah Alexandria ihsin a rami, “Faphir Khawzing,” an timi tangphawlawng kha kan to. Cuih tangphawlawng cu thlatang sung cuih tikulh ih a rak ummi a si.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sirakus khawpi kan thleng ih cutawkah ni thum kan caam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutawkin kan suak sal ih Rezium an timi khua kan thleng. A thaisun ah thlanglam ihsin thli a hung hrang ih ni hnih hnuah Puteoli khua kan thleng.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutawkah zumtu unau pawl an rak um ih an hnenah zarh khat caam dingin in dil. Cule cutawk ihsin Rom khua kan thleng.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Rom ih a ummi zumtu unau pawl in kan thawmvang an theih tikah Appius Dawr an timi khua le Riahbuk Pathum an timi khua tiang in ra hmuak. Paul cu anmah a hmuh tikah Pathian a lawm ih a lungtho in thazaang a ngah ngaingai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Rom khua kan thlen tikah Paul cu amahte in an umter ih ralkap pakhat an kilter.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ni thum hnuah Paul in cutawk hrawngih a ummi Judah upa pawl kha tongkhawm dingah a sawm. An rat tikah Paul in an hnenah, “Ka phunpi Israel mi pawl, kan Israel miphun le kan pupa pawl hnen ihsin kan ngahmi kan nun daan parah zianghman siatsuahnak ka tuah lo naón Jerusalem ah thawng in thlak ih tlunah Rom pawl ih kutah in pe.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thu in sut hnuah thih tlak sualnak zianghman ka tuah lo ti kha an hmu ih Rom pawl cun a thlah in duh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sikhalsehla cumicu Judah mi pawl in an el tikah ka phunpi parah zianghman mawhthluk ding ka nei lo naón Rom siangpahrang hnenih azu khaan lo a theih nawn lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Curuangah nanmah ton le nan hnenih thusim ka duhnak a si. A ngaingai ti ahcun hiti ih thir cikcin ih khih ka sinak cu Israel mi in an ruahsan ringringmi pa ih ruangah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Annih in Paul hnenah, “Na thuhla ah hin Judea ram ihsin cakuat zianghman kan ngahmi a um lo. Na thuhla a sia a ṭha simtu dingah khilam ihsin a ra thlengtu kan milai zohman an um fawn lo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sikhalsehla na ruahnak cu a theih kan duhzet, ziangahtile nan pawl thu hi hmunzakipah mi in an relsia a si ti kan thei,” tiah an ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Curuangah Paul thawn ni an tin aw ih Paul umnak ahcun an ni tin ni ah mi tampi an ra suak. Zing ihsin zan tiang, Pathian Uknak thu cu a simfiang ciamco ih, Moses Daan cabu sung ihsin le profet pawl ih canganmi sung ihsin la tahratin Jesuh ih thu kha an thinlung sungah lut dingin a sim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A simmi in mihrek cu an thinlung a fiangter, asinain mihrek cun an zum lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Paul in thu pakhat a sim ih cuih thu ruangah an lung a rual thei lo ih an ṭiakdarh aw ṭheh. A simmi cu, “Thlarau Thianghlim in, Profet Isaiah hmangin, nan pu le nan pa pawl hnenih a simmi thu cu a dikzet a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A rak simmi cu: ‘Hi minung pawl hnenah va feh awla va sim aw; Nan ngai rero ding naón nan thei lo ding; Nan zoh rero ding naón nan hmu lo ding.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ziangahtile an thinlung a pit, an hna a set ih an mit a caw. Cutin a si lole an mit in an hmu ding; An hna in an thei ding ih, an thinlung in an theithiam ding. Ka lam an hoikir ding ih ka damter hai ding a si, tiah Pathian in a ti,’,” tihi a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cule Paul in a netnak ah, “Pathian ih rundamnak Thuthang cu Zentail mi hnenah thlenter a si zo, tihi nan theih a ṭul a si. Annih in cuih Thuthang cu an ngai ding!” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> (Paul in cutiin a sim ṭheh hnuah Judah mi pawl cu an ṭiak ih anmah le anmah nasa zetin cuih thu-ah an el aw ciamco.)",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Paul cu amahte a saanmi innah kum hnih sung a um. Amah ton duhih a rami hmuahhmuah kha ṭhatein a rak tong.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ralṭhazet le zalen zetin Pathian Uknak thu kha a sim ih Bawi Jesuh Khrih ih thu khal a zirh."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;